nd programmes\n</li>\n<li>Qualitative data from interviews and focus group discussions are usually analyzed by organizing them into key categories and themes\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Identify trends in the data\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Trends:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nRecognize what the trends suggest\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Implications:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Discuss the findings with key stakeholders\"]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nDraw conclusions and make recommendations about the programme\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Recommendations:</p><br>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(749,96,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(750,