v>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Conferences to consider:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Take action</b></p>\n<p>After an evaluation, it is also important to reflect and learn from the things that worked and the things that did not.</p>\n<p>Use the evaluation results to make decisions about:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\n Which aspects of the programme should continue\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\n Which aspects need to be changed\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\n Which aspects should be stopped\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\n Which successful practices could be scaled up\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\n Which other areas and priorities in the community need to be addressed\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\nHow the programme budget should be adjusted in response to planned changes\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(801,98,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(802,98,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(803,98,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is r