bility of many development sectors with which CBR needs to collaborate.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>Identify existing nutrition-based health services</b></p>\n<p>1. Identify health services that can provide proper assessment and management of cases of malnutrition:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-1 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-2 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-3 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-4 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-5 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-6 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-7 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-8 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-9 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-10 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-11 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-12 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-13 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-14 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-15 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<p>2. Identify nutrition initiatives in the communities your organization serves:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-16 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-17 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-18 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-19 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-20 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-21 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-22 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-23 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-24 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-25 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-26 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-27 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-28 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-29 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-103-30 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Train CBR personnel</b></p>\n<p>Provide training to ensure that CBR personnel are able to perform the following tasks:</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-103-31 \"Identify people with signs of malnutrition\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Screening should include all people (both with and without disabilities)</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-103-32 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the health services identified above for proper assessment and management of cases of malnutrition\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-103-34 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the nutrition programmes listed above\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-103-33 \"Ensure that children with disabilities get sufficient and appropriate food to eat\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Children with disabilities are often neglected, especially those with feeding problems</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-103-34 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children with disabilities are actively included in programmes that monitor growth and provide micronutrients and supplementary food\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-103-33 \"Identify people with disabilities who have feeding difficulties, and provide referrals to speech and language therapists where possible\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Children with cerebral palsy can have chewing and swallowing problems, as well as difficulty speaking</p></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-103-33 \"Encourage the use of iron-rich and vitamin-rich foods that are locally available\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Spinach, drumstick leaves, whole grains, papaya fruit</p></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-103-34 class:checkbox \"Demonstrate low-cost, nutritious recipes to encourage people to eat nutritious foods\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-103-34 class:checkbox \"Encourage pregnant women to attend ante-natal care for iron and folic acid supplements\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(888,103,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(889,103,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\"