\n<p>Self-help groups enable people to come together in small numbers to share common experiences, situations or problems with each other. CBR can support the formation and continued success of self-help groups in a number of ways.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify existing self-help groups</b></p>\n<p>Identify existing self-help groups in your community that address specific health needs, such as groups of people with spinal cord injuries, or affected by leprosy, or living with HIV/AIDS, or who are parents of children affected by cerebral palsy.</p>\n<p>As your organization encounters individuals affected by each of these health needs, connect these individuals to the self-help group that is appropriate for them.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Group Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Supported Health Need</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>2. Identify needs for additional support</b></p>\n<p>Identify health needs for which no self-help groups currently exist. For each one, identify individuals(s) affected by this need. When a sufficient number of individuals exist, encourage these individuals to come together to form a new self-help group. (In small villages, it may be difficult to establish such a group and 1:1 support from a peer may be more appropriate.)</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Health Need</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Affected Individual(s)</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n</div>\n<p><b>3. Support self-help groups</b></p>\n<p>Encourage new and existing self-help groups, in partnership with others, to participate actively in health-promoting activities in their communities, including by:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-747 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Organizing health camps\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-747 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Observing World Health Day, World Mental Health Day and the International Day of Persons with Disabilities\"]\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(950,105,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(951,105,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent 