care organizations</b></p>\n<p>Identify health-care organizations in your community that could potentially benefit from learning more about disability.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Organization Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Contact Person</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>2. Provide training to these organizations</b></p>\n<p>Contact each of the organizations above and offer to schedule training classes that include relevant activities from the following list:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox123 class:checkbox \"Orient health workers, such as primary health care personnel) towards disability and inform them of the challenges faced by people with disabilities and their families\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox124 class:checkbox\"Help health workers understand the importance of communicating with people with disabilities in a respectful and nondiscriminatory manner and provide them with practical demonstrations to facilitate learning\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox125 class:checkbox \"Show health professionals how they can make simple adaptations to interventions to ensure that their health messages are understood\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox126 class:checkbox \"Encourage health professionals to use a variety of media and technologies when planning and developing health information and programmes for people with disabilities\"]'),(992,108,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"