anizations listed above:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox211 class:checkbox \"Ensure that specific health promotion programmes and services are physically accessible for people with disabilities\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Create partnerships between urban, social and health planners and people with disabilities so they can work together to create and improve physical and architectural accessibility\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Urban planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p><p>Social planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text102 class:textarea ]</p><p>Health planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text103 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Create opportunities to enable people with disabilities to participate in recreational activities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Possible activities (e.g. support wheelchair users to organize a wheelchair football match)</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Ensure accessible and safe public transport\"]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Provide education and training to address any misconceptions, negative attitudes and stigma that exist within the health sector and community towards people with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Existing misconceptions, negative attitudes and stigma:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Organize cultural events to address problematic health issues within the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Possible events (e.g. dance, drama, songs, films, puppet shows)</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>'),(1011,110,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1012,110,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1013,110,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is requ