mple and straightforward with basic language and relevant pictures.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Are materials accessible?</strong></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Local health promotion programmes and services</b></p>\n<p>Identify local health promotion programmes and services that people with disabilities can contact for additional information, training and support.</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Programme or Service Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>2. Connect people with disabilities with the health promotion resources they need</b></p>\n<p>Visit people with disabilities and their families in their homes, and identify their specific needs for health-related knowledge and skills. Then:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Distribute relevant health promotion materials\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Provide information about how to contact relevant health promotion programmes and services\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox113 class:checkbox \"Talk about how to maintain a healthy lifestyle, giving practical suggestions\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Assist people with disabilities and their families to engage assertively and confidently with health-care providers so they can ask questions and make decisions about their health\"]\n\n<p><b>3. Develop and provide additional customized training (as needed)</b></p>\n<p>Visit people with disabilities and their families in their homes, and identify their specific needs for health-related knowledge and skills. Then:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Develop specific education sessions, if necessary, for people with disabilities whose needs are not being met by those targeting the general community\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Provide training for individuals with disabilities, in partnership with the health sector, to enable them to become health promotion educators\"]\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1126,118,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1127,118,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1128,118,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"acc