v class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-7 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-8 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-9 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-10 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-11 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-12 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-13 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-14 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-15 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Contact each of these services and provide advice on access issues faced by pregnant women with disabilities:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-667 id:cf-131-16 class:checkbox \"Provide suggestions about appropriate communication methods\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-667 id:cf-131-17 class:checkbox \"Provide advice on how to make hospitals and delivery rooms accessible\"]\n<p>2. Identify <b>genetic counseling services</b> available in the communities that your organization serves:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-18 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-19 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-20 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-21 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-22 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-23 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-24 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-25 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-26 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-27 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-28 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-29 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-30 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-31 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-32 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<p>3. Identify training programmes for traditional birth attendants in the communities you serve:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-32 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-33 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-34 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-35 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-36 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-37 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-38 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-39 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-40 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-41 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-42 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-43 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-44 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-45 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-46 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-130-22 class:checkbox \"Contact each of these training programmes and ensure that they include information on disability and the early recognition of impairments\"]\n<p><b>Support people with disabilities</b></p>\n<p>Provide women and their families with the following types of support:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-47 class:checkbox \"Provide all women with information about the maternal health services listed above, and encourage them to access these\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-48 class:checkbox \"Provide additional support for women with disabilities when access to maternal health-care services might be difficult\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><b>Example:</b> Provide advocacy where discrimination exists in the health-care system</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-49 class:checkbox \"Refer women and their families for genetic counselling when they have specific questions or concerns related to current or future pregnancies\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><b>Example:</b> A couple with a disabled child might ask if their next child will inherit the same condition/impairment.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-50 class:checkbox \"Encourage families to register children with disabilities with the local authorities at birth so they can receive appropriate services\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!--\n<p><b>Train CBR personnel</b></p>\n<p>Provide training to ensure that CBR personnel are able to perform the following tasks:</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-52 \"Identify people with signs of malnutrition\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Screening should include all people (both with and without disabilities)</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2 \">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-53 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the health services identified above for proper assessment and management of cases of malnutrition\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-54 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the nutrition programmes listed above\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-55 \"Ensure that children with disabilities get sufficient and appropriate food to eat\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Children with disabilities are often neglected, especially those with feeding problems</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-56 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children with disabilities are actively included in programmes that monitor growth and provide micronutrients and supplementary food\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-57 \"Identify people with disabilities who have feeding difficulties, and provide referrals to speech and language therapists where possible\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Children with cerebral palsy can have chewing and swallowing problems, as well as difficulty speaking</p></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical  p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-58 \"Encourage the use of iron-rich and vitamin-rich foods that are locally available\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Spinach, drumstick leaves, whole grains, papaya fruit</p></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-59 class:checkbox \"Demonstrate low-cost, nutritious recipes to encourage people to eat nutritious foods\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-60 class:checkbox \"Encourage pregnant women to attend ante-natal care for iron and folic acid supplements\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1174,131,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s: