intro\"> \n<h5><b>Build relationships with medical-care providers</b></h5>\n<p>Medical personnel often have limited knowledge about disability and how best to enable access for people with disabilities to medical-care services. By making contact with medical services and building relationships with staff, CBR can develop a network that can be used to facilitate referrals and comprehensive medical care for people with disabilities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>Communicate directly with medical personnel</b></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Promote awareness among medical personnel about the health needs of people with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage medical personnel to involve people with disabilities and their family members in the development of medical treatment and care plans\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Work jointly with community health programmes to ensure that people with disabilities can access the benefits of these programmes\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Facilitate communication between medical personnel and others</b></p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Organize interactive sessions between individuals and groups of people with disabilities, family members and medical personnel to enable discussion of key issues related to disability and sharing of experiences\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Example topic</b>: Access issues</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Request that medical services provide education and training for CBR personnel\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Suggested topics</b>: How to:\n<ul>\n<li>Assist with early detection</li>\n<li>Provide referrals to appropriate services and</li>\n<li>Provide follow-up in the community</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1461,158,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1462,158,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1463,158,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12: