s to access medical care and support.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify medical service providers</b></p>\n<p><b>Local providers</b></p>\n<p>Identify existing medical service providers in your local area. (Be sure to include government, private and non-governmental service providers, as well as providers of traditional medicine, if appropriate.)</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Services offered</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Is location accessible?</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-1 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-2 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-3 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5 ]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:cf-138-4 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-5 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-6 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-7 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-8 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5 ]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutto