ss=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-45 id:text class:cf-227-2 ]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Distribute resource materials</b></p>\n<p>Create mechanisms for making resource materials available to the people who need them.</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-934 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Give resource materials to all CBR personnel to carry with them when visiting people with disabilities for rehabilitation\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-934 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Create resource centres where people with disabilities, family members and other members of the community can go to pick up resource materials\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>: Resource centres may be located in:\n<ul><li>Local development offices</li>\n<li>Community health centres</li>\n<li>Centres for people with disabilities</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n\n</div>'),(1681,227,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your