ss=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Speech therapists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Audiologists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Mobility trainers</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Prosthetists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Orthotists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Medical and paramedical personnel</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Training for rehabilitation personnel</b></p>\n<p>CBR staff should also provide education to rehabilitation personnel to raise their awareness about the following topics.</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"The role of CBR\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"How CBR can help them optimize their services\"]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1712,229,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1713,229,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1714,229,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too