<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"The purpose and function of assistive devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note: </b>This can be provided by:\n<ul>\n<li>Research information or training available on the internet, or from non-governmental organizations</li>\n<li>Trained professionals, such as physiotherapists</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Which basic devices can be prepared in the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> Crutches, walking sticks, picture boards\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Where specialized devices are available\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b>  Prostheses, hearing aids\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Who to contact to access specialized devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"The funding options available for people who are unable to afford devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Practical knowledge</b></p>\n<p>Practical training is also essential, particularly for CBR personnel who work in rural or remote areas, to ensure they can produce basic assistive devices and develop the skills and confidence to work directly with individuals who need the devices. For example, CBR personnel may need to:</p>\n\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox p-2\"Show a family how to build a wooden chair with a strap to enable a child with poor balance to sit upright\"] \n\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Show a family how to build parallel bars to enable walking practice at home\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Show a family how to make a simple walking stick for a person recovering from a stroke to assist him or her in walking\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Teach a child with cerebral palsy, with no speech or coordinated hand movement, how to use a pictorial communication board using his or her eyes\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Provide instruction to a blind person on the use of his or her white cane\"]\n[submit]\n</div>'),(1725,231,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1726,231,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1727,231,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There