and try assistive devices will assist them in making informed decisions\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Use their assistive devices properly and safely to achieve optimum function\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Perform repairs and maintenance to ensure long-term use\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide feedback to referral services about any difficulties experienced so that adjustments can be made and different options considered\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Prevent secondary complications that may arise from using the devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Note:</b> Self-help groups enable people to share valuable information, experiences and skills like the ones mentioned above. These groups can be particularly beneficial when someone has limited access to rehabilitation personnel.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1801,250,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"addition