xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1825,253,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too short.\";s:12:\"invalid_date\";s:29:\"The date format is incorrect.\";s:14:\"date_too_early\";s:44:\"The date is before the earliest one allowed.\";s:13:\"date_too_late\";s:41:\"The date is after the latest one allowed.\";s:13:\"upload_failed\";s:46:\"There was an unknown error uploading the file.\";s:24:\"upload_file_type_invalid\";s:49:\"You are not allowed to upload files of this type.\";s:21:\"upload_file_too_large\";s:20:\"The file is too big.\";s:23:\"upload_failed_php_error\";s:38:\"There was an error uploading the file.\";s:14:\"invalid_number\";s:29:\"The number format is invalid.\";s:16:\"number_too_small\";s:47:\"The number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\";s:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(1826,253,'_additional_settings',''),(1827,253,'_locale','en_US'),(1830,255,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Identify early childhood development situation</b></h5>\n<p>Identifying early childhood development situation takes a twin-track approach: focus on the system and focus on the child. Many initiatives only work on a single track, focusing on the individual. However, that approach results in only a few children getting the benefit of inclusion. The twin-track method works to change the system as well, helping more children and families.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>1. Focus on the system</b></p>\n<p>To effectively address early childhood education inclusion in the system, CBR should work with families, community leaders, health workers and teachers, and anyone else who is involved.</p>\n<p>First, determine the existing situation in your context. What kinds of resources are available for early childhood education? How many people are making use of those resources? Are there children in need of these resources who are not able to use them? What barriers exist in resources, access, or attitudes? What else can you think of that helps to describe your current situation?</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n<p>Next, continue by identifying some of the people who you may work with:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Families\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify potential families:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Community leaders\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify potential community leaders:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Health workers\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify potential health workers:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Teachers\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify potential teachers:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Others\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify anyone else who may be involved:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Determine the existing situation for early childhood care and education in the community.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Describe the situation:\n[text text-257 id:cf-255-2 class:cf-255-2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Identify who is included or excluded in the current system.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify who is included or excluded:<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Included</b><br>[text text-209 id:cf-255-3 class:cf-255-3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Excluded</b><br>[text text-209 id:cf-255-4 class:cf-255-4]</div>\n </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Identify the strengths and weaknesses of the existing system.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify strengths and weaknesses:\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Strengths</b><br>[text text-209 id:cf-255-3 class:cf-255-3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Weaknesses</b><br>[text text-209 id:cf-255-4 class:cf-255-4]</div>\n </div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>2. Focus on the child</b></p>\n<p>A second track is to focus on the child. To do so, your programme will need to develop a system that can identify and support children who:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Are at risk of being marginalized or excluded\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"style=\"width: 100%;\">Identify potential children:\n<br>[textarea textarea-994 id:cf-255-45 class:cf-255-45 cols:60 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Might need additional support\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"style=\"width: 100%;\">Identify potential children:\n<br>[textarea textarea-994 id:cf-255-45 class:cf-255-45 cols:60 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>3. Continuing to support both focuses</b></p>\n<p>After you have identified your starting points for working with the system and with the individual children, your programme can start deeper work with families and the community. The following tips will help your programme to focus on all these stakeholders:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Liaise and work with health workers to ensure that children with disabilities receive proper health care.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><b>Note:</b> For more information, see the Health module.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Ensure that early identification programmes support children with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"style=\"width: 100%;\">What are some early identification programmes that your organisation may need to work with to ensure this? <br>[textarea textarea-315 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 rows:3 cols:50]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Work closely with families to ensure that children who are born with impairments, or who develop them in early childhood, are identified as early as possible\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"style=\"width: 100%;\">What mechanisms, stakeholders, or partners can you draw on to ensure that you quickly identify all children who might need services? <br>[textarea textarea-315 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 rows:3 cols:50]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Support parents to respond quickly when impairments have been identified, referring children to health-care facilities and accompanying the parents to appointments\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"style=\"width: 100%;\">Identify the health-care facilities in your community, and any special services available such as pediatric care:\n <br><div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><b>Health-care facility</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><b>Special services?</b></div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[text text-810 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1]</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\" style=\"width: 100%;\">[text text-810 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),(1832,255,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1834,255,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1836,255,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too short.\";s:12:\"invalid_date\";s:29:\"The date format is incorrect.\";s:14:\"date_too_early\";s:44:\"The date is before the earliest one allowed.\";s:13:\"date_too_late\";s:41:\"The date is after the latest one allowed.\";s:13:\"upload_failed\";s:46:\"There was an unknown error uploading the file.\";s:24:\"upload_file_type_invalid\";s:49:\"You are not allowed to upload files of this type.\";s:21:\"upload_file_too_large\";s:20:\"The file is too big.\";s:23:\"upload_failed_php_error\";s:38:\"There was an error uploading the file.\";s:14:\"invalid_number\";s:29:\"The number format is invalid.\";s:16:\"number_too_small\";s:47:\"The number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\";s:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(1838,255,'_additional_settings',''),(1840,255,'_locale','en_US'),(1904,257,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Support early learning in the home</b></h5>\n<p>Early childhood care and learning begins at home. Therefore, family involvement is essential. Parents play a crucial role in their childs development in the early years. Your organization can help support early learning in the home by involving families and promoting home-based activities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>1. Preparation</b></p>\n<p>First, think about what kinds of activities could be undertaken in the home. Think about the typical activities already done in homes in your community which are or could be made appropriate for children in this age range.</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n<p><b>2. Involve families</b></p>\n<p>Parents play a crucial role in children\'s development during the early years. Mothers in particular can influence their child\'s development through their attitudes and behavior, such as breastfeeding or spending time stimulating and playing with their child. Fathers\' involvement is also important and should be encouraged. Some possible activities include:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Support families in communicating knowledge about their children, gained from their roles as parents, siblings, grandparents, etc., to teachers and health workers. Families can provide a great resource for CBR personnel to learn from\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Provide support, education and training for families to enable them to care for and provide positive learning opportunities for their disabled children\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Assist families to access specialized training if needed or specialized services to assist with skill development\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> \n<ul>\n<li>Sign language training to facilitate communication with deaf children</li>\n<li>Occupational therapy</li>\n<li>Physiotherapy</li>\n<li>Speech therapy</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Develop individual learning plans for children with disabilities in cooperation with families, utilizing their personal and detailed knowledge as well as the CBR personnel\'s knowledge of child development and assessment.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> These plans can be shared with teachers where appropriate\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1  \"Form self-help groups for parents of children with disabilities, or encourage parents to join existing groups or associations. Sometimes parents are members of disabled people\'s organizations\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Are there any self-help groups or disabled people\'s organizations already in your community?\n[textarea textarea-459 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Create support networks and linkages between family members, the community and local resource people\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Respond to gender issues that may be present in families, such as to encourage families to allow girls with disabilities to access learning opportunities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>What are some additional ways that your programme can encourage family involvement and are consistent with the culture of your community?</p>\n[textarea textarea-459 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 rows:5 cols:150]\n\n<p><b>3. Promote home-based activities</b></p>\n<p>Creating a supportive learning environment for children in the home is a key activity for CBR. Inclusion in the family is promoted through building confidence and skills, and facilitating early stimulation for the child. Here are some suggested activities for CBR. Use the list below as a starting point for developing additional activities that make sense for your organization.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage parents to involve their children in activity-based learning in creative and lively ways\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example:</b> \n<ul><li>Learning simple math concepts (e.g., first, second, third) by helping with cooking</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Show how everyday objects found in the home and local environment can be used for play, and show how play equipment can be made at home; even children with severe impairments do not always require \'specialist-made\' equipment\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example:</b> \n<ul><li>Pots and cooking implements can be used to make lively sounds</li>\n<li>Small objects in a basin of mud make interesting sensory toys</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Show how assistive devices can be made by family members using local materials\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example:</b> \n<ul><li>Seating aids</li>\n<li>Mobility aids</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Take care not to focus exclusively on the child\'s impairment and physical needs (for example, a child with physical impairment may be given a lot of input, training and education related to mobility). Be sure to attend to social skills that also need to be developed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples of social skills:</b> \n<ul><li>Potential to play with non-disabled peers</li>\n<li>Potential to learn alongside non-disabled peers</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage for families to do at home in your community?</p>\n[textarea textarea-459 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 rows:5 cols:150]\n</div>'),(1905,257,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1906,257,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1907,257,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too short.\";s:12:\"invalid_date\";s:29:\"The date format is incorrect.\";s:14:\"date_too_early\";s:44:\"The date is before the earliest one allowed.\";s:13:\"date_too_late\";s:41:\"The date is aft