eckbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to take their children on outings into the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> \n<ul>\n<li>Religious/faith based activities</li>\n<li>Social activities such as shopping</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to allow children to play outside the house, with support from special seating or assistive devices if needed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Explore how the community can help to construct or provide assistive devices.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage children with and without disabilities to play together\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Mutual learning between siblings and between neighborhood children is important and helpful.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Involve the local community in making the environment more accessible and welcoming, including the preschool and local playground\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples of facilities to provide:</b> \n<ul>\n<li>Ramps</li>\n<li>Toilets</li>\n<li>Increased lighting</li>\n<li>Improved safety</li>\n<li>Cleanliness</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage families to do at home in your community?</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n\n</div>'),(1923,259,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email