that government guidelines on accessibility are respected</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Get help from family members and volunteers as support in the classroom, taking care to ensure that their support is for the whole class and not just for the child with a disability\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify family members and others as possible classroom volunteers:<br>[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Set learning targets that are achievable and relevant to their lives\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify opportunities to observe children learning at home and in the classroom:<br>[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage families to do at home in your community?</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n</div>'),(1936,261,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1937,261,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sen