g on early childhood intervention approaches and activities. Early childhood personnel, such as teachers, support staff, and administrators in day centres, preschools, play groups, etc. need to learn about disability and inclusion.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify training and awareness-raising needs</b></p>\n<p>First, identify the training and awareness-raising needs in your community. People in need of training or awareness-raising may include CBR personnel, early childhood personnel, the community at large, or more. What information or skills do they need to move toward more inclusive approaches to early childhood education? Are there attitudes that may need to be challenged, and if so, what are effective ways to do this?</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Persons or groups</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Types of training or awareness-raising needed</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>2. Identify sources of support</b></p>\n<p>In order to best support the training and awareness-raising for each group of people, you can connect with people who are able to provide support, whether financial or technical. Use the space below to generate some possible types and sources of support. Consider local, national and international non-governmental organizations as appropriate.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Person or organization; contact information</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Types of support provided</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Connect with these potential sources of support, and set up either a group or individual meeting with them to help them better understand the groups of people identified in step 1, and the training and awareness-raising needs they have.</p>'),(1983,269,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1984,269,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s