e following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify resources</b></p>\n<p>Identify the United Nations organizations, non-governmental organizations, and government services that could help in a time of crisis:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Organization</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Area of focus</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>2. Network and prepare for future emergency</b></p>\n<p>Next, take steps to connect and work with these organizations to prepare for situations of emergency. In particular, work with these partners to think about and prepare for ways to sustain early childhood education during these crises. For more information about preparing for and responding to humanitarian crises, see the see the Humanitarian Crises portion of the Supplementary module.</p>\n\n</div>'),(2005,273,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your