ber format is invalid.\";s:16:\"number_too_small\";s:47:\"The number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\";s:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(2515,334,'_additional_settings',''),(2516,334,'_locale','en_US'),(2518,336,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Address poverty</b></h5>\n<p>Children from extremely poor families are among the most excluded from primary education, and children with disabilities are usually members of these families.</p>\n<p>However, while poverty is a significant barrier to primary education, experience shows that negative attitudes are a much bigger barrier to inclusion than poverty. Sometimes inclusion is more successful in poor communities because people are accustomed to overcoming difficulties, working together and looking after one another.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p><b>To help address issues related to poverty, CBR programmes can:</b></p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that families are supported in feeding their children, or that schools provide a meal a day for schoolchildren\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Your programme may partner with other non-governmental organizations or government services to provide these means</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Develop contacts with local authorities, charities, businesses or other non-governmental organizations to encourage the donation of food, uniforms and educational materials\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">List local authorities, charities, businesses, or other organizations in the region who may be able and willing to assist in this effort:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Strengths</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Needs (of child)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Challenges</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Needs (of family)</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Work closely with families to determine their real concerns, and then mobilize the community to offer support\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Facilitate the family\'s involvement in income-generating activities so children can access education instead of helping the family make a living\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> For more information, see the <a href=\"/livelihood\">Livelihood module</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Emphasize the importance of inclusion even when resources are limited\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Example:</b> <ul><li>Even when there is no school building and students meet under a tree, children with disabilities can join in</li>\n<p>Ways to do this may include:</p>\n<li>Holding conversations with individuals or groups in the community</li>\n<li>Raising awareness through publications and events</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For more information, see the <a href=\"/empowerment\">Empowerment</a> module.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Help find creative solutions for transporting children with disabilities who are not able to go to school alone and whose parents have no time to accompany them\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Example:</b> <ul><li>Other students (peer support), grandparents, neighbours or other community members can be encouraged to take the children to and from school</li>\n<li>Local businesses or non-governmental organizations may be able to offer assistance by providing transport</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2519,336,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2520,336,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpres