invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(2522,336,'_additional_settings',''),(2523,336,'_locale','en_US'),(2548,338,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Network, advocate and share information</b></h5>\n<p>To promote inclusive education, the education sector needs to be transformed at community, district and national levels. Inclusion will not be sustainable without supportive policies, budgets, structures and managers. CBR can help by networking and creating alliances, lobbying groups and establishing partnerships with many different types of groups and organizations.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Education is a central issue for donors, governments and development agencies, so there are many different target groups for lobbying. They include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>National offices of donor agencies (e.g. the World Bank and the European Union)</li>\n<li>International non-governmental organizations involved in education</li>\n<li>District and national governments, and</li>\n<li>Ministries of education</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The importance of information cannot be overemphasized. CBR programmes can play a key role in disseminating information and resources on inclusive education.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Look internally</strong></p>\n<p>In addition to working with external groups, it is important to look within the current school system. Take this opportunity to assess the situation by answering the following questions:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Do staff members accept and respect each other? (Consider gender, class, caste, ethnicity, socio-economic background, etc.)</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What are the existing attitudes about inclusion among the schools staff?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What are the existing attitudes about inclusion among the parents and other community members involved in the school?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What other aspects of the school do you want to assess?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>After you have answered these questions, what are some practical steps that your programme can take to support the staff, parents, and other members in the educational system? Some of the practical steps may be done in conjunction with the external groups in the next step.</p>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:135 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>2. Look externally</strong></p>\n<p>What are some of the outside groups that your organisation could aim to work with? What actions could you take together? Look back to the actions you listed in the previous step. Are there any that could be taken with an external group identified here?</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Organization and contact information</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><b>Possible actions</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\">[text text-828 id:text1 class:text12]</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),(2549,338,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2550,338,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2551,338,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying t