><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p><b>To facilitate community involvement in secondary and higher education, CBR can:</b></p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage the community and school authorities to organize transport facilities  this may require requesting financial assistance from credit groups and practical support from self-help/self-advocacy groups\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b>  For more information about credit groups, see the <a href=\"livelihood\">Livelihood module</a> For more information about self-help and self-advocacy groups, see the <a href=\"empowerment\">Empowerment module</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Mobilize the community to raise finances for fees, uniforms, assistive devices and additional support\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify the ways that you could use the funds raised by the community:\n[textarea textarea-359 id:textarea12 class:textarea12 cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage the community to recognize students with disabilities as a resource for the community\n\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify the strengths and skills of the students with disabilities to share with the community:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Student</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Strengths and skills</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Gain access to grants, government loans, and funding from donor agencies\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some existing grants, loans and funding options from government services or other donor agencies:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Source of possible funding</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Requirements for applications</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:22 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Work with local disabled peoples organizations to facilitate lobbying and the formation of advocacy groups to promote the rights of students with disabilities in secondary and higher education\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Note: For more information about lobbying and advocacy, see the <a href=\"/empowerment\">Empowerment module.</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>What are some other ways that you can involve your community to support students with disabilities to access secondary and higher education?</p>\n[textarea textarea-54 id:textarea1 class:textarea12 cols:130 rows:4]\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2578,340,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2579,340,'_