le','en_US'),(2666,346,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Encourage best use of specialist resources and support</b></h5>\n<p>CBR can encourage schools and colleges to use specialist resources correctly, thereby increasing the inclusion of students with disabilities rather than increasing their stigmatization or segregation.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>Your organisation can encourage best use of specialist resources such as the following:</b></p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage the community and school authorities to organize transport facilities  this may require requesting financial assistance from credit groups and practical support from self-help/self-advocacy groups\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Examples:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Guides</li>\n<li>Readers</li>\n<li>Writers</li>\n<li>Interpreters</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Itinerant teachers who make regular visits to schools to provide advice and support\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Additional support outside the mainstream school\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples of types of support to provide:\n<ul>\n<li>Computer skills</li>\n<li>School staff</li>\n<li>Local government</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2667,346,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUD