:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(2704,353,'_additional_settings',''),(2705,353,'_locale','en_US'),(2747,356,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Ensure community-based day centres are age-appropriate</b></h5>\n<p>Community-based day centres are often established to provide respite for parents who have children with disabilities needing 24-hour care. While these centres may be a great support for parents, often the quality of activities and learning for children is very poor. CBR programmes can help ensure that the centres provide age-appropriate play and activity-based learning, and that the best interests of the child are the priority. The centres should also be as inclusive as possible, and involve local children without disabilities and their parents.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Assess the existing situation at the community-based day centres in your area. What sorts of activities do children participate in at the centre? Are the activities age-appropriate for the children? Are children with disabilities included?</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Day centre name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Age of children</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Activities</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Are activities age-appropriate?</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Are children with disabilities included?</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>For any activities that are not age-appropriate or inclusive, work with the day centre staff and caretakers to implement changes. The following activities can be helpful:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-662 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \n \"Hold training sessions for caretakers and parents to learn about age-appropriate or inclusive activities.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Invite parents to demonstrate age-appropriate and inclusive activities.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-662 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \n \"Hold informational sessions for caretakers and parents to learn more about disabilities and how they can help children with disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-662 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \n \"Work with caretakers at the day centre to build physical accommodations if needed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2748,356,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient