opments and be equipped to help people with disabilities to take advantage of them.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p><b>1. Identify opportunities</b></p>\n<p>Identify existing opportunities for continuing education, particularly through distance learning. Assess whether each one is inclusive of adults with disabilities. If not, work with the staff and leaders of the programmes to become more inclusive. Investigate any national requirements for accessibility of online resources and make programme developers aware of those requirements. Your organisation may offer trainings or staff support to help their staff better understand disability and the needs of students with disabilities.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Programme name</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact person(s)</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Type of programme (in-person, distance)\n</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Topics of focus or credentials offered\n</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Inclusive of adults with disabilities (Y/N)\n</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><b>2. Work with institutions to enrol students with disabilities</b></p>\n<p>Identify students who have an interest in continuing education and what their specific topics of interest are. Working with the students, reach out to the programmes that they are interested in and gather information about what is required for enrolment. Work with the programmes to gather all the necessary documents and information from the students and their families, and to facilitate the application and enrolment process.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Student</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Programme of interest</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Requirements for enrolment</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Documents and information required</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Additional requirements</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>3. Provide support for students with disabilities</b></p>\n<p>Provide support for students who are enrolled or wish to enrol in continuing education, as well as for people with disabilities who may not know about the continuing education opportunities available to them. Use this list as a starting point for developing support programmes or informational sessions for students and potential students.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-430 id:cf-244-1 class:cf-244-1 \"Conduct informational meetings about the types of continuing education opportunities available\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b><p>If possible, invite representatives of the programme(s) or current or past students of the programme as guest speakers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-430 id:cf-244-1 class:cf-244-1 \"Offer training to equip students with specific skills and help build their confidence\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some specific training topics that would be most useful for the students with disabilities in your community.\n[textarea textarea-921 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:50 rows:3]\n<p>Examples of topics to consider:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Study skills</li>\n<li>Time management skills</li>\n<li>Introduction to distance learning</li>\n<li>How to use specific software</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-838 id:cf-321-1 class:cf-321-1 \"Assist adults with disabilities to obtain the support they need to participate in these programmes\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Students may require either physical or technical supports to access the courses in their programme. Examples may include:\n<ul>\n<li>Large print</li>\n<li>Braille</li>\n<li>Computer</li>\n<li>Access to the internet</li>\n<li>Computer screen reading software</li>\n<li>Voice to text software</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Identify the specific supports that students with different types of disabilities will need for their programmes:</p>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Disability type</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme of</br>interest</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:10 rows:1 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 c