\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-838 id:cf-321-1 class:cf-321-1 \"Identify opportunities to share this information with other members of the community\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Information can be shared with others in many ways (e.g. in print or verbally). Identify opportunities where many people in the community might be reached, including:\n<ul>\n<li>Town or community meetings</li>\n<li>Activities open to the community</li>\n<li>Job listing boards</li>\n<li>Town square</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Opportunity</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Time/date</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Method of sharing the information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\