option for many people with disabilities. If an individual chooses this option, it is essential that he or she undergoes appropriate business-skills training.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify business-skills training opportunities</b></p>\n<p>Identify local programmes that offer business-skills training. Note that small-enterprise development training programmes often offer this type of training; these can be found in many countries, and are often linked to microfinance schemes</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Training programme name</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Skill(s) taught</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Barrier(s) to the participation of students with disabilities</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact person</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[t