ent types of disabilities can participate\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide suggestions on how the organizations facilities and services could be adapted to better meet the needs of students with disabilities\"]\n\n<b>Provide support to students with disabilities</b>\n<p>Identify and meet with students with disability who are interested in vocational training, and provide each student with the following types of support.</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Help students identify the training and education programme(s) best suited to their needs\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide support to facilitate students participation in these programmes (e.g. transport, sign language interpretation, materials)\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Periodically follow up with students to check on their progress, providing additional support as needed\"]\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2920,381,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2921,381,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2922,381,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too short.\";s:12:\"invalid_date\";s:29:\"The date format is incorrect.\";s:14:\"date_too_early\";s:44:\"The date is before the earliest one allowed.\";s:13:\"date_too_late\";s:41:\"The date is after the latest one allowed.\";s:13:\"upload_failed\";s:46:\"There was an unknown error uploading the file.\";s:24:\"upload_file_type_invalid\";s:49:\"You are not allowed to upload files of this type.\";s:21:\"upload_file_too_large\";s:20:\"The file is too big.\";s:23:\"upload_failed_php_error\";s:38:\"There was an error uploading the file.\";s:14:\"invalid_number\";s:29:\"The number format is invalid.\";s:16:\"number_too_small\";s:47:\"The number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\";s:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(2923,381,'_additional_settings',''),(2924,381,'_locale','en_US'),(2928,384,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Facilitate training in mainstream institutions</b></h5>\n<p>CBR should promote access to mainstream training opportunities in vocational training centres for people with disabilities, and work with both training centres and students to overcome any barriers to participation.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Skills development by people with disabilities is more effective when it takes place in an inclusive environment. Training in mainstream vocational training institutions usually offers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A greater choice of skills training opportunities</li>\n<li>Access to newer technologies and equipment</li>\n<li>Formal certification upon completion of training</li>\n<li>Career guidance, and</li>\n<li>Job placement assistance</li>\n</ul>\n<b>1. Identify formal training centres</b>\n<p>Begin by identifying formal vocational training centres in the communities that your organization serves. Note that such training centres are often located in towns and cities and are geared to the skills needs of larger urban enterprises. But there are also many local government, non-governmental organization, community-operated and private vocational training centres in rural areas with courses that provide useful training in technical and core life skills.</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Training centre name</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Skill(s) taught</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Barrier(s) to the participation of students with disabilities</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact person</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<b>2. Encourage training centres to increase accessibility</b>\n<p>CBR should encourage and facilitate vocational training centres and courses to increase access for people with disabilities. For example, centres can be encouraged to:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Adopt an enrolment policy that sets a specific target number of women and men with disabilities to be enrolled at each intake\n\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Set flexible entry requirements\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide remedial basic education courses\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide guidance to trainees with disabilities on the different skills development options available, avoiding disability- and gender-based stereotypes\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide disability-awareness training to instructors\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide fact sheets on the special needs of trainees with different types of disabilities\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Determine the accessibility and adaptation needs of individual trainees (e.g. trainees using wheelchairs may be easily integrated if training courses are on the ground floor and toilet facilities are accessible)\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Arrange for support during training to assist trainees with disabilities to succeed, and help instructors and trainees resolve any difficulties that may arise\"]\n\n<b>3. Encourage people with disabilities</b>\n<p>CBR programmes should also take steps to encourage people with disabilities to apply for training in vocational training centres, including the following:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Meet with parents, community groups and others to raise their awareness about the importance of vocational skills training for people with disabilities\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Publicize the availability of places for trainees with disabilities to local schools, disabled peoples organizations, parents associations, non-governmental organizations, and womens and youth organizations\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Support trainees with disabilities in applying for enrolment and for financial aid\"]\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2929,384,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2930,384,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2931,384,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One