ify unmet demand for the production of goods and provision of services in the community\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Upgrade the curriculum, tools and equipment used in training courses, in consultation with local enterprises\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Increase the number and variety of courses offered\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide training not only in technical skills, but also in business management and life skills\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Provide support to trainees who have successfully completed their training in finding work or becoming self-employed\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox22 \"Raise funds for new courses and equipment, as well as the expansion of the centre(s)\"]\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(2938,386,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2939,386,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(2940,386,'_messages','a:23:{