rket analysis.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<b>1. Identify unmet or partially-met needs</b>\n<p>Become familiar with the needs of the potential market, and identify one or more needs that are not currently being met, or that are only partially being met.</p>\n<em>Identifying an unmet need often requires thinking beyond the obvious (including possibly looking beyond local demand).</em>\n<b>Unmet or partially-met need:</b>\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n\n\n<b>2. Study the technology required to meet the need</b>\n<p>Identify the product(s) that would satisfy the unmet need, and investigate the technology that would be required to produce it/them, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Necessary production equipment</li>\n<li>Required skills</li>\n<li>Physical demands of the work</li>\n</ul>\n<b>Product/Production technology required:</b>\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n[textarea textarea-963 id:textarea class:textarea122 cols:130 rows:4]\n\n<b>3. Identify the interests and capabilities of business participants</b>\n<p>Become familiar with the interests and capabilities of the individuals or groups who would participate in the business as either owners or employees.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Individual/Group:</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Interests:</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Capabilities:</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n<