y sources of support</b>\n<p>Identify sources of support available from family members.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Family member</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Support</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>4. Provide guidance</b></p>\n<p>As needed:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-663 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Encourage individuals or parents of children with disabilities to join a group income-generation activity, if appropriate\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-663 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Pay particular attention to assisting women with disabilities find ways to generate an income\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-663 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Help successful entrepreneurs with disabilities become trainers of other people with disabilities\"]\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button ty