12 \"Become familiar with national and local employment laws and policies that affect people with disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Summarize significant findings in a format that is easy to understand and that can be easily distributed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b><p>This information can be extremely helpful in educating employers about:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The rights of people with disabilities</li>\n<li>The obligations of businesses</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Where no laws and policies currently exist, work with people with disabilities and their organizations to advocate for them\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<b>2. Identify potential allies</b>\n<p>Identify and contact businesses that already have a proactive policy of employing people with disabilities and use them as examples.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Business name</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Location</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact name</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact Information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Identify and collaborate with individuals and groups in the disabled community, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Prominent individuals with disabilities (who can serve as role-models)</li>\n<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\n<li>Disability activists</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Student</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Programme of interest</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Requirements for enrolment</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n<b>3. Make the case</b>\n<p>Work with DPOs to plan and conduct publicity drives to encourage employers of all sizes to consider employing people with disabilities. Explain the reasons why, including:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Employers of disabled workers consistently report that people with disabilities perform equally well or better than their non-disabled peers in productivity, safety and attendance\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Lower cost of job turnover; people with disabilities are often more likely to stay in the job than their peers\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"People with disabilities have skills that businesses need: both technical job skills and transferable problem-solving skills developed in daily life\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Corporate social responsibility is increasingly important to many businesses, which feel they should give back to the community or the customers who have made their business a success\"]\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3015,404,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3016,404,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3017,404,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"inva