-367 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Become informed of all legal provisions related to discrimination in housing\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-367 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Make sure that people with disabilities who are seeking housing are informed of their rights\"]\n<b>Identify housing agencies</b>\n<p>1. Identify <b>public sector agencies</b> within the communities in your area that are responsible for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Enforcing housing-related (including anti-discrimination) regulations</li>\n<li>Overseeing the construction and/or management of public housing developments</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Agency</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Domain</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Responsibility</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-1