.</i></p>\n<p><b>Providing training for people with disabilities</b></p>\n<p>People with disabilities may need training to help them gain the confidence and skills they need to identify and manage their personal assistance needs. They may require training in communication and assertiveness skills to enable them to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Express their needs and expectations to their personal assistant(s)</li>\n<li>Effectively negotiate their personal assistance needs within their families, communities, schools and workplaces</li>\nThey may also require assistance in learning how to:\n<li>Identify, arrange and manage their personal assistance</li>\n<li>Train their personal assistant(s)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Identify training opportunities that are already available, and share information with individuals with disabilities who require training and their families.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 w-25\"><strong>Training resource name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 w-25\"><strong>Resource type</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 w-25\"><strong>Type(s) of training provided</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 w-25\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5 class:w-100]</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-25\">\n<div class=\"p-1\">[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Disabled peoples organization\"]</div>\n<div class=\"p-1\">[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Self-help group\"]</div>\n<div class=\"p-1\">[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Government service\"]</div>\n<div class=\"p-1\">[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Training institute\"]</div>\n<div class=\"p-1\">[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Non-governmental organization\"]</div>