n	<li>A trained representative from a disabled peoples organization</li>\n    <li>A local law enforcement officer, and</li>\n    <li>CBR personnel</li>\n </ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Are there temporary facilities in the community that can be used?\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">If yes, list the facilities\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<p>If no, identify one or more such facilities. Options might be available in facilities that offer respite care or rehabilitation.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Is there a safe hostel in the community for supporting women or girls who have experienced sexual abuse or domestic violence?\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">If yes, specify facility contact information:\n[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:5]\nIf no, work with local authorities to provide one.\n<b>Note:</b> These facilities need to be modified if necessary to ensure access for women and girls with disabilities. \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Do social workers and other counselors who support families in crisis situations also have training in disability?\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">If no, specify information about available trainings. If there are no such trainings yet available, identify the topics that may be needed, and identify potential CBR staff who can support the trainings:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Training programme or topic</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Can disabled peoples organizations and CBR identify families who are willing to provide support and care for other families experiencing a crisis?\n\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">If yes, identify the support families:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div></div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div></div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\nFor more information about crises situations, visit Supplementary module: Humanitarian Crises.\n\n\n\n\n</div>'),(3273,488,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3274,488,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3275,488,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditio