our organization can do to facilitate movement away from institutional care. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>Identify existing alternatives to institutional care</b></p>\n<p>If alternatives to institutional care already exist in your country, identify and list these below.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">Organization name</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Disability type(s) served</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<b>Work to support the provision of new alternatives</b>\n<p>If there are no local alternatives to institutional care  or if there are an insufficient number of these alternatives  work with institutions and relevant government departments to provide new alternatives.</p>\n<p>Identify institutions to contact.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Institution name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Identify relevant government departments to contact.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Department name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Department responsibilities</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<b>Note:</b> Countries that have moved away from institutional care have successfully converted these institutions into alternative facilities, such as:\n<ul>\n	<li>Vocational training and resource centres</li>\n	<li>Rehabilitation centres</li>\n	<li>Independent housing, where people with disabilities can live independently with some support available as needed</li>\n	<li>Respite accommodation, where people with disabilities stay for short breaks while family members take a break from their roles as personal assistants</li>\n	<li>Emergency accommodation for all members of the community (and not just for people with disabilities) who are vulnerable to violence</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<!------\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What are the sanitation facilities like?\n<ul>\n<li>Are toilets private, clean and accessible to all, including students with disabilities and young women?</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Is there clean water available for washing and drinking?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Is there sufficient light in the rooms?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Are there clear notices and signboards around the school?\n<ul>\n<li>Are these adapted so that visually-impaired students can use them?</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Are there any other items to note about the school?</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea rows:5 cols:35]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>2. Taking action</b></p>\n<p>Now what are some practical steps that you could take with the local primary school to create an accessible environment? Work with school administrators and other personnel to implement these changes. Remember that a welcoming environment is more than just ramps and other physical supports. For example, a school can be made more welcoming by:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Putting up posters and drawings showing positive images of students with and without disabilities from different backgrounds and ethnicities</li>\n<li>Developing policies promoting tolerance and condemning bullying</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-281 id:cf-331-1 class:cf-331-1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3303,491,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3304,491,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"