s and abilities.</p>\n<p>CBR can work with families to promote independence for family members with disabilities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox pias_check1 id:cf-513-1 class:checkbox \"Provide information and support to address their concerns regarding their members with disabilities, as well as for their own position and status within the community.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify specific concerns that families in your community have regarding their family members with disabilities, and their own position and status in the community.\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Family name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Specific concerns to address</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea fa_r1c1 id:cf-513-2 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</divlass=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea scta_r1c2 id:cf-513-3 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea fa_r2c1 id:cf-513-4 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</divlass=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea scta_r2c2 id:cf-513-5 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea fa_r3c1 id:cf-513-6 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</divlass=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea scta_r3c2 id:cf-513-7 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea fa_r4c1 id:cf-513-8 class:textarea cols:18 rows:2]</divlass=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[te