yle=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox lpwd_check1 id:cf-517-1 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to appropriate support networks in the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Support networks may include:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\n		<li>Self-help groups</li>\n	</ul>\nIdentify potential support networks for people with disabilities in your community:\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Group type</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gn_r1c1 id:cf-517-2 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gt_r1c2 id:cf-517-3 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciii_r1c3 id:cf-517-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gn_r2c1 id:cf-517-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gt_r2c2 id:cf-517-6 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciii_r2c3 id:cf-517-7 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gn_r3c1 id:cf-517-8 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea gt_r3c2 id:cf-517-9 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciii_r3c3 id:cf-517-10 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea fa_r4c1 id:cf-517-11 class:tex