rmat is invalid.\";s:16:\"number_too_small\";s:47:\"The number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\";s:16:\"number_too_large\";s:46:\"The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\";s:23:\"quiz_answer_not_correct\";s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(3378,519,'_additional_settings',''),(3379,519,'_locale','en_US'),(3385,521,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h4><b>Promote the use of culture and art for social change</b></h4>\n<p>Disability advocacy and awareness campaigns are often more effective when based on locally relevant cultural and artistic media. Because of this, CBR should use these media to achieve social change for disability.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>CBR programmes can work with local artists and producers to organize drama, arts and music events that challenge disability stigma and discrimination in the community.</p>\n<p><b>Identify issues to address</b></p>\n<p>First, identify the types of stigma and discrimination that are present in the community:</p>\n[textarea tom_r2c1 id:140-6 class:textarea rows:4 cols:97]\n<b>Identify artists</b>\n<p>Next, identify artists in your community who may be willing and able to help address these issues.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Artist name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Medium (dance, music, etc.)</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r5c1 id:cf-140-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<b>Identify projects to promote social change</b>\n<p>Work with the artists listed above to identify ways they could use their skills such as drama, visual art, or music events to challenge stigma and discrimination.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Idea</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Stigma or discrimination to target</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Artists or participants involved</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>People with disabilities involved</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r1c3 id:140-3 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r1c4 id:140-4 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r1c5 id:140-5 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea tom_r2c1 id:140-6 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r2c3 id:140-8 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r2c4 id:140-9 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r2c5 id:140-10 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea tom_r3c1 id:cf-140-11 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r3c3 id:cf-140-13 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r3c4 id:cf-140-14 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r3c5 id:cf-140-15 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea tom_r4c1 id:cf-140-16 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-17 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r4c4 id:cf-140-19 class:textarea rows:4 cols:21]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableC