lowing chart to guide their individual reflection. When family members feel ready, it may be useful for CBR staff members to work with them to help generate ideas of how to challenge their fears.</p>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>My fears or worries</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Why do I think this?</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>What are some things I can do about this?</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r1c1 id:cf-519-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r1c2 id:cf-519-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r1c3 id:cf-519-6 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r2c1 id:cf-519-10 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r2c2 id:cf-519-11 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r2c3 id:cf-520-12 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r3c1 id:cf-519-13 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r3c2 id:cf-519-14 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r3c3 id:cf-519-15 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox pfitw_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Put families in touch with others who share similar experiences and concerns\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\nIdentify organizations (e.g. local disabled peoples organizations, violence prevention networks) with which your organisation can work to disseminate information.\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Family name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Experiences</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Concerns</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r1c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r1c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r1c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r2c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r2c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r2c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r3c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r3c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cfwl_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Connect families with local self-help groups, or other similar support organizations\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\nIdentify existing organizations in your community:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Area of focus</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text grpna_r1c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf_r1c2 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text loc_r1c3 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text aof_r1c4 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text grpna_r2c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf_r2c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text loc_r2c3 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text aof_r2c4 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text grpna_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf_r3c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text loc_r3c3 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text aof_r3c4 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<b>Note:</b> If no self-help groups currently exist, work with families with family members who have disabilities to create them.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cfwl_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Connect families with local disabled peoples organizations\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Examine any misconceptions families may have, and</li>\n	<li>Increase their confidence, expectations and aspirations</li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\nIdentify disabled peoples organizations in or near your community:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Organization name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text on_r1c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coi_r1c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text on_r2c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coi_r2c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text on_r3c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coi_r3c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>'),(3401,526,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3402,526,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\"