r activities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>To promote the inclusion of people with disabilities in religious and spiritual activities, CBR can:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox srlad_check1 id:cf-533-1 class:checkbox1 \"Sensitize religious leaders about disability, and the importance of including people with disabilities in religious and spiritual activities\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\n<p>Identify religious leaders with whom you can work</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Leader name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Religious affiliation</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text leana_r1c1 id:cf-533-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text relaf_r1c2 id:cf-533-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text leana_r2c1 id:cf-533-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text relaf_r2c2 id:cf-533-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text leana_r3c1 id:cf-533-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text relaf_r3c2 id:cf-533-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox pfitw_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Work with religious leaders to challenge discriminatory or harmful practices towards people with disabilities in the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Work with leaders to identify the types of discriminatory or harmful practices that need to be addressed.\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Discriminatory or harmful practices</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disoha_r1c1 id:cf-533-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disoha_r2c1 id:cf-533-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disoha_r3c1 id:cf-533-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox etpwd_check1 id:cf-533-11 class:checkbox \"Ensure that people with disabilities have access to personal assistance to enable them to attend religious/spiritual services and programmes\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\n<p>Identify people with disabilities in your community who may need personal assistance. Take steps to ensure that they have the support they need:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name of person with disabilities</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Type(s) of personal assistance needed</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text nowdis_r1c1 id:cf-533-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text topan_r1c1 id:cf-533-13 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text nowdis_r1c1 id:cf-533-14 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text topan_r1c1 id:cf-533-15 class:text class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text nowdis_r1c1 id:cf-533-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text topan_r1c1 id:cf-533-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox patla_check1 id:cf-533-18 class:checkbox \"Provide advice and assistance to leaders about making information accessible\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\nExamples:\n<ul>\n	<li>Make prayers, songs, chanting, and sermons accessible with signed translation</li>\n\n	<li>Make religious texts available in large print, audio and Braille</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox wwlte_check1 id:cf-533-19 class:checkbox \"Work with leaders to ensure that:\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Places of worship are physically accessible, and</li>\n    <li>Religious practices are modified to accommodate people with disabilities</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\n<p>Identify people with disabilities in your community who may need personal assistance. Take steps to ensure that they have the support they need:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Leader name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Religious affiliation</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Accommodations needed</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text lenam_r1c1 id:cf-533-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text relaffi_r1c2 id:cf-533-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text accnee_r1c3 id:cf-533