one number is invalid.\";}'),(3428,533,'_additional_settings',''),(3429,533,'_locale','en_US'),(3433,535,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h4><b>Identify local recreation, leisure and sports opportunities</b></h4>\n<p>A first step is to find out what recreation, leisure and sporting opportunities already exist in and around the community.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Begin by identifying the recreation, leisure and sporting opportunities in and around the communities your programme serves. Work closely with community groups like the following to do this:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>Youth groups</li>\n	<li>Womens groups</li>\n	<li>Childrens clubs</li>\n	<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Description of activity</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Current participants</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Sponsoring group(s)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text doact_r1c1 id:cf-535-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text cupar_r1c2 id:cf-535-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text spogrp_r1c3 id:cf-535-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf_r1c4 id:cf-535-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text doact_r2c1 id:cf-535-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text cupar_r2c2 id:cf-535-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2