<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h4><b>Use recreation and sport to raise awareness about inclusion</b></h4>\n<p>Major events such as the International Day of Disabled Persons often attract positive media attention. Because of this, they can raise awareness across a wide audience from the national to local level about the need for inclusive recreation and sporting activities.</p>\n\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<b>Step 1: Identify events</b>\n<p>Identify major events held in your community that could serve as platforms to raise awareness.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Event</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact person(s)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Who is involved?</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Who is their typical audience?</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text evet_r1c1 id:cf-539-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conson_r1c2 id:cf-539-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wiinv_r1c3 id:cf-539-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text witta_r1c4 id:cf-539-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text evet_r2c1 id:cf-539-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conson_r2c2 id:cf-539-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wiinv_r2c3 id:cf-539-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text witta_r2c4 id:cf-539-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text evet_r3c1 id:cf-539-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conson_r3c2 id:cf-539-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wiinv_r3c3 id:cf-539-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text witta_r3c4 id:cf-539-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text evet_r4c1 id:cf-539-13 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conson_r4c2 id:cf-539-14 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wiinv_r4c3 id:cf-539-15 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text witta_r4c4 id:cf-539-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<b>Step 2: Identify messages</b>\n<p>Work with people with disabilities and their families to identify the important messages that your organisation aims to spread through these major events.</p>\n[textarea idmsg_r1c1 id:cf-539-17 class:textarea rows:4 cols:100]\n\n<b>Step 3: Create a plan</b>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[checkbox wwtciis_check1 id:cf-539-18 class:checkbox \"Work with the contacts identified in step 1 to develop solutions for disseminating the messages identified in step 2.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Be sure to consider how people with disabilities and their families can be ambassadors for inclusion.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n  </div>'),(3448,539,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"r