rm to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>The first priority should always be to focus on working with mainstream organizations to ensure that their programmes are accessible and inclusive. However, in some cases it may be necessary to develop independent disability-specific recreation, leisure and sports programmes. These types of programmes can be very effective in:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Helping people with disabilities to increase their confidence and skills</li>\n	<li>Raising awareness about disability</li>\n	\n</ul>\n<b>Set up new programmes and organizations</b>\n<p>CBR programmes should identify people with disabilities who can serve as leaders and play strong roles in the decision-making process during the development of new recreation and sports programmes that are suitable for people with disabilities.</p>\n<p>People with disabilities who can serve as leaders:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Area(s) of interest</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible role(s)</strong></div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text nam_r1c1 id:cf-544-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoi_r1c2 id:cf-544-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text prs_r1c3 id:cf-544-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text nam_r2c1 id:cf-544-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoi_r2c2 id:cf-544-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text prs_r2c3 id:cf-544-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text nam_r3c1 id:cf-544-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoi_r3c2 id:cf-544-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text prs_r3c3 id:cf-544-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text nam_r4c1 id:cf-544-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoi_r4c2 id:cf-544-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text prs_r4c3 id:cf-544-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Identify people with disabilities who are interested in setting up their own recreation and sports groups or clubs. Determine what their area(s) of interest are, and what supports, such as training or funding, they might need.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Name of person</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Area(s) of interest</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Training needed</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Other resources needed</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text namofp_r1c1 id:cf-544-13 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text asoi_r1c2 id:cf-544-14 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text trnee_r1c3 id:cf-544-15 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text otrrene_r1c4 id:cf-544-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text namofp_r2c1 id:cf-544-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text asoi_r2c2 id:cf-544-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text trnee_r2c3 id:cf-544-19 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text otrrene_r2c4 id:cf-544-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text namofp_r3c1 id:cf-544-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text asoi_r3c2 id:cf-544-22 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text trnee_r3c3 id:cf-544-23 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text otrrene_r3c4 id:cf-544-24 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text namofp_r4c1 id:cf-544-25 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text asoi_r4c2 id:cf-544-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text trnee_r4c3 id:cf-544-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text otrrene_r4c4 id:cf-544-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<b>Connect with national and international organizations</b>\n<p>Link local disability recreation and sports groups/clubs to national and international organizations, such as:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>International Sports Federation for People with Intellectual Disability</li>\n    <li>International Paralympic Committee</li>\n    <li>Special Olympics International</li>\n    <li>International Committee of Sports for the Deaf</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Identify local recreation and sports groups/clubs:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group or club name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Area(s) of focus</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grporcl_r1c1 id:cf-544-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoffo_r1c2 id:cf-544-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coinfo_r1c3 id:cf-544-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grporcl_r2c1 id:cf-544-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoffo_r2c2 id:cf-544-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coinfo_r2c3 id:cf-544-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grporcl_r3c1 id:cf-544-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoffo_r3c2 id:cf-544-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coinfo_r3c3 id:cf-544-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grporcl_r4c1 id:cf-544-38 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asoffo_r4c2 id:cf-544-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text coinfo_r4c3 id:cf-544-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Identify national and international organizations to link with these local community groups:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Level (national, international)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Area(s) of focus</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Local group(s) to connect with</strong></div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grpnam_r1c1 id:cf-544-41 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cotinfo_r1c2 id:cf-544-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lelni_r1c3 id:cf-544-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asofus_r1c4 id:cf-544-44 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lgtcw_r1c5 id:cf-544-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grpnam_r2c1 id:cf-544-46 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cotinfo_r2c2 id:cf-544-47 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lelni_r2c3 id:cf-544-48 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asofus_r2c4 id:cf-544-49 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lgtcw_r2c5 id:cf-544-50 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text grpnam_r3c1 id:cf-544-51 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cotinfo_r3c2 id:cf-544-52 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lelni_r3c3 id:cf-544-53 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asofus_r3c4 id:cf-544-54 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lgtcw_r3c5 id:cf-544-55 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text  grpnam_r4c1 id:cf-544-56 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cotinfo_r4c2 id:cf-544-57 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text lelni_r4c3 id:cf-544-58 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text asofus_r4c4 id:cf-544-59 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div c