an help to better understand them.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox lhlae_check1 id:cf-546-2 class:checkbox1 \"Learn how laws are enforced\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Local law enforcement officers are valuable resources understand how to report a crime, and identify protection mechanisms that are in place for victims and witnesses.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox irbfanf_check1 id:cf-546-3 class:checkbox \"Identify resources (both formal and non-formal) available in your community to assisting people with disabilities accessing justice\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\n<p>Identify resources available in your community:</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Resource</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text resour_r1c1 id:cf-546-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninfom_r1c2 id:cf-546-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text resour_r2c1 id:cf-546-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninfom_r2c2 id:cf-546-7 class:text class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text resour_r3c1 id:cf-546-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninfom_r3c2 id:cf-546-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text resour_r4c1 id:cf-546-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninfom_r4c2 id:cf-546-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<p>Note: Examples include:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>Local leaders (government, tribal, village and religious leaders)</li>\n	<li>Teachers</li>\n	<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\n	<li>Medical professionals</li>\n	<li>Unions and cooperatives</li>\n	<li>Law enforcement and court personnel</li>\n	<li>Legal aid services</li>\n	<li>Community legal centres</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button> \n\n  </div>'),(3469,546,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3470,546,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3471,546,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\