\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox wwbtecw_check1 id:cf-554-34 class:checkbox \"Work with banks to enable clients with disabilities to manage their own accounts, and access credit\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify banks in your community below. Note whether each one is already inclusive; and, if not, what additional support the bank may require.\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Bank name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Inclusive? (Y/N)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Support needed</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text bnkna_r1c1 id:cf-554-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conion_r1c2 id:cf-554-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text incyn_r1c3 id:cf-554-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text supnded_r1c4 id:cf-554-38 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text bnkna_r2c1 id:cf-554-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conion_r2c2 id:cf-554-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text incyn_r2c3 id:cf-554-41 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text supnded_r2c4 id:cf-554-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text bnkna_r3c1 id:cf-554-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conion_r3c2 id:cf-554-44 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text incyn_r3c3 id:cf-554-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text supnded_r3c4 id:cf-554-46 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text bnkna_r4c1 id:cf-554-47 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text conion_r4c2 id:cf-554-48 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text incyn_r4c3 id:cf-554-49 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text supnded_r4c4 id:cf-554-50 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<b>Note:</b> CBR personnel may need to provide training on disability and inclusion for bank staff.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox sslifldtm_check1 id:cf-554-51 class:checkbox \"Support sign language interpreters for local doctors to make it easier for hearing-impaired individuals to access and use health-care facilities\"]\n	<ul>\n		<li>Manage their own accounts, and</li>\n		<li>Access credit</li>\n			</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify potential sign language interpreters in your community.\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Years of experience</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text eman_r1c1 id:cf-554-52 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text continf_r1c2 id:cf-554-53 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text yerofexp_r1c3 id:cf-554-54 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text eman_r2c1 id:cf-554-55 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text continf_r2c2 id:cf-554-56 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text yerofexp_r2c3 id:cf-554-57 class:text class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text eman_r3c1 id:cf-554-58 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text continf_r3c2 id:cf-554-59 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text yerofexp_r3c3 id:cf-554-60 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text eman_r4c1 id:cf-554-61 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text continf_r4c2 id:cf-554-62 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text yerofexp_r4c3 id:cf-554-63 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<P>Now, identify local doctors who could benefit from working with a sign language interpreter.</P>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text eman_r1c1 id:cf-554-64 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conatcti_r1c2 id:cf-554-65 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text eman_r2c1 id:cf-554-66 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conatcti_r2c2 id:cf-554-67 class:text class:w-100]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text eman_r3c1 id:cf-554-68 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conatcti_r3c2 id:cf-554-69 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text eman_r4c1 id:cf-554-70 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conatcti_r4c2 id:cf-554-71 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<b>Note:</b> CBR personnel can work with both the interpreters and doctors to facilitate the start-up process, and familiarize the interpreter with any technical and medical terminology.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox wwtarar_check1 id:cf-554-72 class:checkbox \"Work with tribal and religious leaders and heads of families to enable people with disabilities to claim their inheritance rights\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify tribal and religious leaders and heads of families in your community below. Note what type of support each individual may require.\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Affiliated group(s)</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Supports needed</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text emna_r1c1 id:cf-554-73 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninn_r1c2 id:cf-554-74 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text affgrp_r1c3 id:cf-554-75 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text supded_r1c4 id:cf-554-76 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text emna_r2c1 id:cf-554-77 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninn_r2c2 id:cf-554-78 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"r