 situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Which of the following methods will most effectively support the needs of the disabled individuals your organization serves to advocate for themselves? Select the methods that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to a strategy that you have selected.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox ipwd_r1c1 id:cf-570-1 class:checkbox \"Include people with disabilities in decision-making for CBR\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox ppwiat_r1c1 id:cf-570-2 class:checkbox \"Provide people with information about their disability\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify information sources:\n[textarea ideis_r1c2 id:cf-570-3 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox ppwiat_r1c1 id:cf-570-4 class:checkbox \"Provide people with information about the services that exist in their communities.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify available services:</p>\n[textarea iaserv_r1c2  id:cf-570-5 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox pitpwd_r1c1 id:cf-570-6 class:checkbox \"Provide information to people with disabilities about their rights\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify information sources:\n[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox lpwdts_r1c1 id:cf-570-8 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to self-help groups.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify self-help groups:</p>\n[textarea idesegr_r1c2 id:cf-570-9 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox tpatsm_r1c1 id:cf-570-10 class:checkbox \"Teach people about the social model of disability\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify information sources:</p>\n[textarea ideins_r1c2 id:cf-570-11 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3524,570,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3525,570,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3526,570,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\"