<p>Which of the following methods will your organization need to undertake to ensure that CBR personnel are effective communicators? Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to a method that you have selected</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage a communication-friendly environment\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox spwcdd_r1c1 id:cf-572-2 class:checkbox \"Support people with communication difficulties to express themselves\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox stslada_r1c1 id:cf-572-3 class:checkbox \"Speak the same languages and dialects as the local communities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify language(s) & dialect(s) that need to be supported:\n[textarea iladtn_r1c2 id:cf-572-4 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox ktlslah_r1c1 id:cf-572-5 class:checkbox \"Know the local sign language, and how to use alternative ways of communicating\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify alternate means of communicating that need to be supported:</p>\n[textarea iamof_r1c2  id:cf-572-6 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox uartdol_r1c1 id:cf-572-7 class:checkbox \"Understand and respect the diversity of local culture\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify local differences that need to be taken into account:\n[textarea ildtntbt_r1c2 id:cf-572-8 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox bagrbc_r1c1 id:cf-572-9 class:checkbox \"Be a good role-model by communicating respectfully with everybody\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox crwdvs_r1c1 id:cf-572-10 class:checkbox \"Communicate regularly with various stakeholders in the health, education, livelihood and social sectors\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify stakeholders in the <b>health</b> sector:</p>\n[textarea isit_r1c1 id:cf-572-11 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\nIdentify stakeholders in the <b>education</b> sector:\n[textarea isites_r1c1 id:cf-572-12 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\nIdentify stakeholders in the <b>livelihood</b> sector:\n[textarea isitls_r1c1 id:cf-572-13 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\nIdentify stakeholders in the <b>social</b> sector:\n[textarea isitss_r1c1 id:cf-572-14 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox fddsm_r1c1 id:cf-572-15 class:checkbox \"Facilitate dialogue during stakeholder meetings\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox khtutmf_r1c1 id:cf-572-16 class:checkbox \"Know how to use the media for communicating with the public\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential media outlets:\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3531,572,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\