area idpotrer_r1c2 id:cf-577-14 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox filmes_r1c1 id:cf-577-15 class:checkbox \"Films\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential resources:\n	[textarea iprs_r1c2 id:cf-577-16 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox redio_r1c1 id:cf-577-17 class:checkbox \"Radio\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential resources:\n	[textarea iprdoe_r1c2 id:cf-577-18 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox wallwrti_r1c1 id:cf-577-19 class:checkbox \"Wall writing\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential resources:\n	[textarea iprets_r1c2 id:cf-577-20 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Note: When working to raise awareness about disability in the community, it is important to remember:</p>\n<ul><li>Messages need to show people with disabilities in a positive light. (Positive role-models help to change mindsets and break habits.)</li><li>Messages should be simple</li><li>The methods used should be appropriate to the local culture</li><li>Awareness-raising activities will have a greater impact when people with disabilities are directly involved in implementing them\n</li><li>Attitudes and behaviours take time to change and is an ongoing process</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3552,577,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-messa