ass=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text potio_r1c2 id:cf-574-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r2c1 id:cf-574-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<b>4. Meet regularly with representatives from all political affiliations</b>\n<p>CBR programmes need to be nonpartisan. They should not subscribe to, or be thought to subscribe to, a particular party or power-base. It is therefore important to meet regularly with representatives of all political affiliations</p>\n<p>List the political affiliations -- and at least one representative of each -- with whom your organization will need to keep in touch</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Political Affiliation</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Representative(s)</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text potio_r1c2 id:cf-574-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r2c1 id:cf-574-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3592,589,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3593,589,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: 