";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(3595,589,'_additional_settings',''),(3596,589,'_locale','en_US'),(3599,591,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Facilitate development of political awareness in the community</b></h5>\n<p>Many persons with disabilities may not be aware how to vote; or they may be unaware of the existence of national laws regarding disability rights or international conventions, such as the CRPD.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify strategies your programme can use to encourage political participation in the disabled community you serve. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Which of the following methods will be most effective in encouraging political participation of persons with disabilities in the community? Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to a method that you have selected.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage adults with disabilities to join literacy programmes\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential literacy programmes:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that people with disabilities have access to advocacy and rights-based training\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential training programmes:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to self-help groups and disabled peoples organizations, where they can learn skills that will be useful for political participation, like public speaking, problem-solving, and campaigning\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Public speaking</li>\n	<li>Problem-solving, and</li>\n	<li>Campaigning</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential self-help groups:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n<p>Identify potential disabled people\'s organizations:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children and adolescents of different impairments are included in activities where they have the opportunity to:\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Express their opinions</li>\n	<li>Think and make decisions, and</li>\n	<li>Understand the consequences of their actions</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3600,591,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3601,591,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz