form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Raise disability awareness within the political system</b></h5>\n<p>Another part of the strategy towards enabling people with disabilities to participate in politics is to develop disability awareness within political systems.</p>\n<p><em>Some activities that can help with this effort are listed below. Select the one(s) that are likely to be most effective in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p>Which of the following methods will be most effective in addressing lack of knowledge about disabilities within government?	Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to a method that you have selected.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Make local political representatives and government officials aware that legislation related to disability exists\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify individuals to contact:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Conduct disability-awareness training with local councils (with people with disabilities taking leadership roles)\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify councils in need of training:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Involve political leaders and representatives in activities carried out by CBR and people with disabilities. Possible activities include inviting them to provide training on available government programmes and to participate in events celebrating the International Day of Persons with Disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Political leaders to contact:\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n<b>Note:</b> Political leaders and representatives usually want to be seen as contributors to the well-being of their constituents, and CBR programmes need to take advantage of this.\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3607,593,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3608,593,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3609,593,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71: