ve</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p>Which of the following activities will be most effective in reducing or removing barriers to political participation that are faced by people with disabilities?	Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to an activity that you have selected.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Provide recommendations to local authorities about making voting sites and procedures accessible to people with disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify recommendations for making voting more accessible:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Investigate transport options to enable people with disabilities to reach voting venues\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify transport options:</p>\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage electoral commissions and advocacy groups to inform voters with disabilities about their voting rights and what types of assistance are available to enable them to participate\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify types of assistance available to enable people with disabilities to participate:\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Encourage political leaders and parties to develop accessible campaign materials\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> These should include depictions of voters with disabilities.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Identify the political positions and government jobs that are reserved for marginalized groups, and encourage people with disabilities to take apply for them\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify available political positions:\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n	Identify available government jobs:\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3613,595,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3614,595,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3615,595,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";