th with and without disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some common issues:\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\n        <b>Example:</b>\n        <ul><li>Facilitate a discussion about gender discrimination with a womens group and highlight how this issue is shared by all women</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Identify existing members of mainstream self-help groups who are either disabled or have a family member who is disabled. Encourage these people to talk about the issues they face, and put disability on the agenda of their self-help group for discussion\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some potential people:\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\n        \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their families are informed about objectives and goals of relevant mainstream groups\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some potential skill or knowledge gaps:\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\n   		<b>Note:</b> Without the necessary skills and knowledge, people with disabilities may be vulnerable to discrimination\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3633,602,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent 