oup federation in various ways. One key way is to bring together one or two elected representatives from each self-help group.</p>\n<b>1. Identify some potential representatives from each self-help group.</b>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Self-help group</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Potential representatives</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<b>2. Organize and facilitate an initial discussion</b>\n<p>The next step is to have a time and space for an initial discussion between representatives of the self-help groups. During the meeting, CBR personnel can facilitate the conversation and help groups to understand each other. Here are some possible topics of discussion for such a meeting:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>General introductions</li>\n	<li>Describe each groups focus, current work, and goals, and find common ground</li>\n	<li>Highlight any existing joint foci, work, and goals</li>\n	<li>Brainstorm any new joint goals</li>\n	<li>Discuss and list out the possible benefits of working together - e.g. additional resources, connections, and joint influence</li>\n	<li>Identify and discuss next steps in working together</li>\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can modify this suggested list of topics of discussion as needed for the self-help groups that you work with.</p>\n<p>In addition, identify some potential meeting times and locations:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Meeting Date and Time</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Meeting Location</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3648,606,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your