l\"><em>Example:</em> Disabled person does not know of the service provided.</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Advertise that service within the disabled peoples organization.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Disabled person does not have a way to physically access the service due to limited mobility or distance.</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Set up some form of transportation to enable the disabled person to travel to the necessary location.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>