bers of disabled peoples organizations to explain CBR and its key points.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> CBR programmes in the past have ignored disabled peoples organizations in their decisions and work.</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Work on fostering meaningful relationships with members of the disabled peoples organizations, and involve them in your organisation decisions and work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<b>2. Identify some ways that DPOs can support CBR</b>\n<p>Here are some ways that DPOs can support CBR. Select the one(s) that your organization can use; then enter some others of your own.</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Promote CBR at national and international levels as a strategy to mainstream development and ensure the benefits of existing international treaties reach more people with disabilities\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Lobby for inclusion of the CBR strategy in government policies and programmes\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Lobby for the necessary budgetary support\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Mobilize communities by raising awareness about disability and the importance of CBR and encourage them to participate in all aspects of CBR programmes\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Directly implement CBR.\"]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 [textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3667,613,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3668,613,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s: