\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(3683,617,'_additional_settings',''),(3684,617,'_locale','en_US'),(3685,619,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h4><b>Facilitate inclusion in CBR</b></h4>\n<p>The phrase, nothing about us without us applies as much to promoting mental health in CBR as in the other components of the CBR Guidelines. Including people with mental health problems in CBR helps to better identify their needs and their families needs, and subsequently, identify the steps and solutions that can best help to address those needs.</p>\n<p><em>Use the planning tool to get started in promoting mental health in your community. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p>The following activities are suggested to facilitate the inclusion of people with mental health problems in CBR:\n</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that CBR personnel have received accurate training regarding mental health problems and have a positive attitude towards supporting and including people with mental health problems.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What are some training topics that you might plan to focus on in your programme?\n[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:4 class:w-100]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Consult and involve people with mental health problems and their family members in the planning, implementation and monitoring of CBR.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some potential people in your community who have mental health problems and/or their family members who could be involved in your organisation:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Person</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible roles</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"In collaboration with people with mental health problems and their families, identify barriers and possible solutions in meeting basic needs, including:\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Access to health services</li>\n	<li>Education</li>\n	<li>Livelihood and</li>\n	<li>Social security</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some barriers and solutions:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Barriers</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible solutions</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Identify mental health personnel, users of mental health services and/or family members who could be involved as resource persons for training of CBR personnel.\"]\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some potential people:\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Barriers</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible solutions</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible solutions</strong></div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:16 rows:2 cl