s:36:\"The answer to the quiz is incorrect.\";s:17:\"captcha_not_match\";s:31:\"Your entered code is incorrect.\";s:13:\"invalid_email\";s:38:\"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(3689,619,'_additional_settings',''),(3690,619,'_locale','en_US'),(3692,621,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h4><b>Overcome stigma and discrimination in the community</b></h4>\n<p>Public knowledge about mental health problems and the possibility of recovery is very limited. To enable people with mental health problems to participate actively in society, common myths, prejudices and discrimination need to be addressed. CBR can play a key role in doing this.</p>\n<p><em>Use the planning tool to get started in promoting mental health in your community. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n\n<p>This checklist can be used as a starting point for you to think of ways to overcome stigma and discrimination. You can develop your own ideas and add them to this list.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure CBR personnel treat people with dignity and respect at all times.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples\n	<ul>\n		<li>Hold trainings for CBR personnel</li>\n		<li>Define what it means to treat people with dignity and respect together</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Consult and involve people with mental health problems and their family members in the planning, implementation and monitoring of CBR programmes.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some key people in the community who may be able to help deliver positive messages and images about mental health. Some examples of people who may be able to help include influential people such as:\n<ul>\n	<li>Local political leaders</li>\n	<li>Religious leaders</li>\n</ul>\n<p>What are some of the key messages that you would like to deliver through each person?</p>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Key messages</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Make contact with the identified key people and provide them with information about mental health issues in their community.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples\n	<ul>\n		<li>Invite them to be guests of honour at events that your organisation has organized</li>\n		<li>Prepare informational sessions or guides to share with them</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Discuss ways in which the key people can deliver important messages about mental health problems.\"]\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some potential messages or methods of dissemination. Some examples include:\n<ul>\n	<li>Religious leaders can deliver messages when addressing their followers</li>\n	<li>Health care personnel can deliver messages during regular appointments, or through distributing or displaying information through their main centre</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible Messages</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Methods of dissemination</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Identify community members and groups that would most likely have contact with people with mental health problems and are likely to have developed negative assumptions and attitudes.\"]\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some potential people and groups to work with who may have negative assumptions and attitudes. Some examples include:\n<ul>\n	<li>Police officers</li>\n	<li>Health-care personnel</li>\n    <li>Traditional healers</li>\n	</ul>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Make arrangements to provide education and training for community members and groups. Provide accurate information about mental health problems to dispel myths and make people aware that there are effective interventions.\"]\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential locations and times to hold the meeting(s):\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Locations</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Times</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:24 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<p>Identify key information to cover during the training(s). These topics may include:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>Dispelling myths that people with mental health problems are violent or that mental health problems are a curse</li>\n	<li>Medical and psychological interventions are available which can support people to recover from mental health problems</li></ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Promote human rights and challenge, when it happens, discriminatory behaviour that occurs in the community towards people with mental health problems and their family members. Be a good role model and demonstrate positive behaviours.\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Examples:</b>\n<ul>\n	<li>Train CBR personnel to recognize and act against discriminatory behavior</li>\n	<li>Work with community leaders to understand how they can demonstrate positive behaviors and model to the rest of the community</li>\n    	</ul>\n    	<p>What are other behaviors that you want your organisation to demonstrate as positive role-models for the community?</p>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-1 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:48 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n<button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(3693,621,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(3694,621,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nTh