 plan should specify:</p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\nWhat specific tasks are required to complete each planned activity\r\n</li>\r\n<li>When each task will need to be undertaken, with start and finish dates\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Who is responsible for helping to complete each task\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To create a detailed work plan, do one of the following:</p>\r\n<p>1. Download and use one of the following open source computer software programmes:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://community.openproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OpenProject</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://community.openproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OpenProject</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.projectlibre.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ProjectLibre</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> WHO does not specifically recommend or endorse the use of any of the above-mentioned programming tools.</p>\r\n<p>or</p>\r\n<p>2. Complete one copy of the following form for each planned activity.</p>\r\n<b>Planned activity ___________________________________________________</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Task</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Start date</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Completion date</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Person or group responsible</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text1 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text2 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCel