tical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Conduct a meeting\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Meeting attendees could include:</p>\r\n<p>Different types of information are analyzed in different ways. For example:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul><li>People with disabilities</li>\r\n<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\r\n<li>Concerned stakeholders and community members</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Write a formal evaluation report\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Write an article for the local newspaper or professional journal\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Newspapers or journals to consider:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Present a paper at a conference\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Conferences to consider:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Take action</b></p>\r\n<p>After an evaluation, it is also important to reflect and learn from the things that worked and the things that did not.</p>\r\n<p>Use the evaluation results to make decisions about:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which aspects of the programme should continue\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbo