n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text30 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact each of the campaigns listed above and:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-879 id:checkbox1 class:checkbox \"Encourage them to:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Actively target and include people with disabilities</li>\r\n<li>Communicate positive images of people with disabilities, such as by depicting people with disabilities on posters and billboards</li>\r\n<li>Develop materials in formats appropriate for people with disabilities, such as including text captioning and sign language interpretation for all videos</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-879 id:checkbox1 class:checkbox \"Ask them what assistance they may need to achieve these goals\"]\r\n<p><b>2. Identify and contact communication resources in your community</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify resources in your community, such as community spokespersons, newspapers, radio, television and web sites, from whom community members regularly receive information.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Disability-Related Health Issue</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Potential Partner(s)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">