b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify health-care organizations</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify health-care organizations in your community that could potentially benefit from learning more about disability.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Organization Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Contact Person</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>2. Provide training to these organizations</b></p>\r\n<p>Contact each of the organizations above and offer to schedule training classes that include relevant activities from the following list:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox123 class:checkbox \"Orient health workers, such as primary health care personnel) towards disability and inform them of the challenges faced by people with disabilities and their families\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox124 class:checkbox\"Help health workers understand the importance of communicating with people with disabilities in a respectful and nondiscriminatory manner and provide them with practical demonstrations to facilitate learning\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox125 class:checkbox \"Show health professionals how they can make simple adaptations to interventions to ensure that their health messages are understood\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-564 id:checkbox126 class:checkbox \"Encourage health professionals to use a variety of media and technologies when planning and developing health information and programmes for people with disabilities\"]\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Educate health-care providers','','publish','closed','closed','','educate-health-care-providers','','','2019-05-09 05:39:32','2019-05-09 05:39:32','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=108',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(109,1,'2019-05-08 09:14:46','2019-05-08 09:14:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"108\" title=\"Educate health-care providers\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-08 09:14:46','2019-05-08 09:14:46','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/08/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(110,1,'2019-05-08 09:32:00','2019-05-08 09:32:00','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Create supportive environments</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR needs to work with community health centres, hospitals, schools, worksites and recreational facilities and with key stakeholders to create supportive physical and social environments for people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify organizations to contact</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify community health centres, hospitals, schools, worksites and recreational facilities in your community that could potentially benefit from learning how they could better serve people with disabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Organization Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Contact Person</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text2 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text3 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text4 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text5 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text6 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text7 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text8 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text9 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text10 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text11 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text12 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text13 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text14 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text15 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text16 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text17 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text18 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text19 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text20 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text21 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text22 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text23 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text24 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>2. Select activities</b></p>\r\n<p>Select the activities your organization will undertake in collaboration with the organizations listed above:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox211 class:checkbox \"Ensure that specific health promotion programmes and services are physically accessible for people with disabilities\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Create partnerships between urban, social and health planners and people with disabilities so they can work together to create and improve physical and architectural accessibility\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Urban planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p><p>Social planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text102 class:textarea ]</p><p>Health planners:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text103 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Create opportunities to enable people with disabilities to participate in recreational activities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Possible activities (e.g. support wheelchair users to organize a wheelchair football match)</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Ensure accessible and safe public transport\"]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-816 id:checkbox222 class:checkbox \"Provide education and training to address any misconceptions, negative attitudes and stigma that exist within the health sector and community towards people with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><p>Existing misconceptions, negative attitudes and stigma:</p><p>[textarea text-836 id:text101 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div 