educe the risks of developing health problems. This is true for everyone, but is especially important for people with disabiliities and the family members who care for them. It is therefore important for CBR to take steps to promote healthy behaviours among the people they serve.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p>For each of the healthy behaviours listed below, identify:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><b>Informational resources</b>, such as brochures, books, classes, and websites, that can be used to educate people with disabilities and their families about the benefits of healthy behaviours\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Sources of <b>social support</b>, such as mentors, peers, and support groups, that can support and encourage people with disabilities and their families who seek to adopt healthier behaviours\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Healthy behaviour</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Informational resources</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Social support</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Not smoking</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:60 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:60 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Drinking small amounts of alcohol\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea03 class:textarea cols:60 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea04 class:textarea cols:60 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"r