n\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<h5><b>Identify existing health promotion resources</b></h5>\r\n<p>Identify existing health promotion resources that can help people with disabilities and their families acquire new knowledge and skills to remain healthy.</p>\r\n<b>Health promotion materials</b>\r\n<p>Identify and collect copies of existing health promotion materials to distribute to people with disabilities and their family members.</p>\r\n<p>When necessary, adapt these materials to make them accessible to people with disabilities, such as people with an intellectual disability will require materials that are simple and straightforward with basic language and relevant pictures.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Are materials accessible?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</