ns the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"107\" title=\"Untitled\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-10 07:51:28','2019-05-10 07:51:28','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/10/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(134,1,'2019-05-10 10:04:50','2019-05-10 10:04:50','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Help to prevent injuries</b></h5>\r\n<p>Many disabilities are caused by accidents at home, at work or in the community. Often adults and children with disabilities are also at higher risk of injury.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To help prevent injuries, ensure that CBR personnel are trained to perform the following tasks:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-1 \"Identify the major causes of injury in the home and community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Examples:</b> Burns, drowning, road accidents</p> \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-2- class:checkbox \"Identify the groups most at risk of injury\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Examples:</b> Children, people working in hazardous occupations</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-3 \"Create awareness in the community about the common causes of injuries, and how to prevent them\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-4 class:checkbox \"Work with local authorities and community groups regarding actions to take to reduce the occurrence of injuries in the home and community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Example:</b> Ways to prevent injuries during major festivals</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-5 \"Provide suggestions for families about how to prevent injuries in the home\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b>\r\n  <ul>\r\n<li>Watching children when they are near water or open fires\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Keeping poisons locked away and out of reach of children\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Keeping children away from balconies, roof edges and stairs\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Not allowing children to play with sharp objects\r\n</li>\r\n</ul></p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-6 class:checkbox \"Provide education for employers and workers about how to prevent workplace injuries\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Example:</b>  Wear appropriate safety equipment (e.g. shoes, helmets, gloves, earplugs) on construction sites</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-7 class:checkbox \"Provide education for schoolchildren about road safety\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Example:</b> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>How to cross roads safely</li>\r\n<li>Wearing seatbelts in motor vehicles</li>\r\n<li>Wearing helmets when riding bicycles and motorbikes</li>\r\n</ul></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSu