\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-10 10:17:22','2019-05-10 10:17:22','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/10/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(136,1,'2019-05-10 10:38:54','2019-05-10 10:38:54','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Help to prevent secondary conditions</b></h5>\r\n<p>People of all ages with disabilities are at risk of secondary conditions. CBR should promote primary prevention strategies to reduce the likelihood that people with disabilities will develop these conditions.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To prevent secondary conditions, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to perform the following tasks:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-1 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their family members are aware and knowledgeable about the secondary conditions commonly associated with their disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Examples:</b>  People with spinal cord injuries or spina bifida should be aware that they are at a high risk of developing urinary tract infections.</p> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-5 \"Assist people with disabilities and their families to identify strategies that will help prevent secondary conditions from developing\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b>\r\n  <ul>\r\n<li>Adopt healthy lifestyle behaviours (e.g. exercise and good nutrition)\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Have regular health check-ups</li>\r\n<li>Maintain good hygiene</li>\r\n<li>Join self-help groups</li>\r\n</ul></p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-6 class:checkbox \"Ensure that any assistive devices provided to people with disabilities do not create risks for secondary conditions\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Example:</b> Ensure that prostheses fit properly and do not cause red marks that can lead to pressure sores.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered 