'2019-05-13 08:11:09','2019-05-13 08:11:09','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Assist with early identification</b></h5>\r\n<p>Early identification of a medical condition provides the best opportunity for curing or managing it. CBR personnel members who work directly in the community are often in a position to notice the early signs of a condition, and to provide the appropriate medical referral.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR should work with primary health-care personnel to establish a mechanism for the early identification of health conditions and impairments associated with disability.</p>\r\n<p><b>Diseases</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR personnel can identify screening activities aimed at the early identification of common communicable or non-communicable diseases, and provide referrals as needed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Disease</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Early signs or symptoms\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information for screening services\r\n</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Tuberculosis</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Leprosy</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-3 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-4 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class