"> \r\n<h5><b>Ensure access to early treatment</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR can promote and encourage collaboration between people with disabilities, their families and primary health-care workers to increase access to medical-care services at all levels.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To promote and encourage collaboration, CBR staff members should be able to perform the following tasks.</p>\r\n<p><b>Before, during and after medical appointments</b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Advocate for people with disabilities as needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><strong>Example:</strong> CBR personnel who know sign language may accompany deaf persons to health facilities to ensure that they are able to: <ul>\r\n<li>Communicate their needs</li>\r\n<li>Understand the information being provided</li>\r\n<li>Access appropriate treatment</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<p><b>After medical appointments</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Check with health workers to make sure individuals who have been included in screening activities are provided with follow-up medical care if needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox Check with health workers to make sure referrals have been made for individuals who require access to secondary and tertiary levels of health care]</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subj