r their own health by seeking appropriate medical care and making healthy lifestyle choices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that they are able to understand and follow medical advice\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to self-help groups to enable them to learn about self-management by sharing knowledge and skills with others\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Self-help group members can share ideas and experiences around:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>What resources are available for medical care</li>\r\n<li>How to effectively negotiate the health-care system</li>\r\n<li>How to manage existing health conditions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Provide direct support</b></p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Develop or adapt existing materials and publications that provide medical information about health conditions into formats that are appropriate for people with disabilities and their family members\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Be sure to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Use simple language</li>\r\n<li>Use simple sketches or pictures</li>\r\n<li>Translate material into local languages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-n