contact-form-7 id=\"154\" title=\"Promote self-management of chronic conditions\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-14 11:17:47','2019-05-14 11:17:47','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/14/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(156,1,'2019-05-15 06:05:40','2019-05-15 06:05:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"112\" title=\"Facilitate access to existing prevention programmes\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-15 06:05:40','2019-05-15 06:05:40','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/15/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(157,1,'2019-05-15 12:21:12','2019-05-15 12:21:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"154\" title=\"Promote self-management of chronic conditions\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-15 12:21:12','2019-05-15 12:21:12','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/15/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(158,1,'2019-05-15 13:10:30','2019-05-15 13:10:30','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Build relationships with medical-care providers</b></h5>\r\n<p>Medical personnel often have limited knowledge about disability and how best to enable access for people with disabilities to medical-care services. By making contact with medical services and building relationships with staff, CBR can develop a network that can be used to facilitate referrals and comprehensive medical care for people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Communicate directly with medical personnel</b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Promote awareness among medical personnel about the health needs of people with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage medical personnel to involve people with disabilities and their family members in the development of medical treatment and care plans\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Work jointly with community health programmes to ensure that people with disabilities can access the benefits of these programmes\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Facilitate communication between medical personnel and others</b></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Organize interactive sessions between individuals and groups of people with disabilities, family members and medical personnel to enable discussion of key issues related to disability and sharing of experiences\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Example topic</b>: Access issues</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Request that medical services provide education and training for CBR personnel\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Suggested topics</b>: How to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Assist with early detection</li>\r\n<li>Provide referrals to appropriate services and</li>\r\n<li>Provide follow-up in the community</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Build relationships with medical-care providers','','publish','closed','closed','','build-relationships-with-medical-care-providers','','','2019-07-04 12:55:27','2019-07-04 12:55:27','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=158',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(159,1,'2019-05-15 13:11:00','2019-05-15 13:11:00','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"158\" title=\"Build relationships with medical-care providers\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-15 13:11:00','2019-05-15 13:11:00','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/15/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(160,1,'2019-05-15 13:37:26','2019-05-15 13:37:26','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"150\" title=\"Facilitate access to surgical care\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-15 13:37:26','2019-05-15 13:37:26','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/15/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(161,1,'2019-05-16 04:58:37','2019-05-16 04:58:37','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Identify needs</b></h5>\r\n<p>Before making a rehabilitation plan and starting activities, CBR personnel need to carry out a basic assessment with an individual and his or her family members to identify needs and priorities. Assessment is an important skill, so CBR personnel should receive prior training and supervision to ensure competency in this area.</p>\r\n<p><em>This checklist spells out some of the most important tools CBR workers should use to collect the necessary information. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>A skilled assessment professional must be resourceful, collecting information through a variety of different means, including those listed below.</p>\r\n<p><b>Personal interviews and observation</b></p>\r\n<p>To identify a persons rehabilitation needs, it is important to seek answers to the following questions, through observation or direct questioning of the individual, his or her family members and other members of the community who are familiar with the individual.</p>\r\n<p>1. What activities can this individual do and not do?</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Can do:</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Can\'t do</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-1 rows:3 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-2 rows:3 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>2. What does the individual want to be able to do?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-3 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>3. What problems do they experience? How and when did these problems begin?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Problem</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>When and how did this problem begin?</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-4 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-5 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-6 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-7 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-8 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-9 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>4. What areas are affected (e.g. body, senses, mind, communication, behavior)?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-10 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>5. What secondary problems are developing?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-11 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>6. What is their home and community situation like?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>7. In what way(s) have they adjusted to their disability?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n\r\n<p><b>Other sources of information</b></p>\r\n<p>In addition to observing and conducting discussions with the individual and his or her family members, useful information can also be obtained from the following sources:</p>\r\n<p>1. Review past medical records, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>2. Perform a basic physical examination of the individual, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-13 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>3. Conduct discussions with involved health professionals/services, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-14 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p><b>Note</b>: It is important to keep a record of the initial assessment and future consultations, so an individuals progress can be monitored over time.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Identify needs','','publish','closed','closed','','untitled-14','','','2019-07-04 13:13:40','2019-07-04 13:13:40','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=161',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(162,1,