:59:25','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Provide training</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR personnel need training to ensure they are able to facilitate access to rehabilitation services and provide appropriate services at community level.</p>\r\n<p><em>Use the planning tool below to think through how your organization might best be able to provide training to your CBR personnel. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Many CBR organizations have developed suitable training programmes.</p>\r\n<p><b>Training for CBR workers</b></p>\r\n<p>One of the most important things CBR workers need to know are the roles of the different personnel involved in providing rehabilitation services.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>What they do</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>How they benefit people with different impairments</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Physiotherapists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Occupational therapists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Speech therapists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Audiologists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Mobility trainers</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Prosthetists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Orthotists</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Medical and paramedical personnel</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Training for rehabilitation personnel</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR staff should also provide education to rehabilitation personnel to raise their awareness about the following topics.</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"The role of CBR\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"How CBR can help them optimize their services\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Provide training','','publish','closed','closed','','provide-training','','','2019-07-04 13:20:08','2019-07-04 13:20:08','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=229',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(230,1,'2019-05-21 10:59:56','2019-05-21 10:59:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"229\" title=\"Provide training\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-21 10:59:56','2019-05-21 10:59:56','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/21/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(231,1,'2019-05-21 11:37:08','2019-05-21 11:37:08','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Train CBR personnel</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR personnel require training on assistive devices to ensure that they are able to provide accurate information, referrals and education.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following checklist to make sure you are able to provide training on all of the key information staff members need to know about assistive devices. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR needs to take steps to ensure that staff members have a thorough understanding of assistive devices, including mechanisms for obtaining specialized devices, manufacturing techniques for simple devices, and the skills needed to support people who need assistive devices learn how to use them.</p>\r\n<p><b>General knowledge</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR personnel need to know about:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"The purpose and function of assistive devices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note: </b>This can be provided by:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Research information or training available on the internet, or from non-governmental organizations</li>\r\n<li>Trained professionals, such as physiotherapists</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Which basic devices can be prepared in the community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> Crutches, walking sticks, picture boards\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Where specialized devices are available\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b>  Prostheses, hearing aids\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Who to contact to access specialized devices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"The funding options available for people who are unable to afford devices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Practical knowledge</b></p>\r\n<p>Practical training is also essential, particularly for CBR personnel who work in rural or remote areas, to ensure they can produce basic assistive devices and develop the skills and confidence to work directly with individuals who need the devices. For example, CBR personnel may need to:</p>\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox p-2\"Show a family how to build a wooden chair with a strap to enable a child with poor balance to sit upright\"] \r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Show a family how to build parallel bars to enable walking practice at home\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Show a family how to make a simple walking stick for a person recovering from a stroke to assist him or her in walking\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Teach a child with cerebral palsy, with no speech or coordinated hand movement, how to use a pictorial communication board using his or her eyes\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-38 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox  p-2\"Provide instruction to a blind person on the use of his or her white cane\"]\r\n[submit]\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Train CBR personnel','','publish','closed','closed','','untitled-17','','','2019-07-04 13:24:46','2019-07-04 13:24:46','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=231',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(232,1,'2019-05-21 11:37:34','2019-05-21 11:37:34','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"231\" title=\"Untitled\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-21 11:37:34','2019-05-21 11:37:34','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/21/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(234,1,'2019-05-25 15:17:48','2019-05-25 15:17:48','<div style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"home-btn-wrapper\"><a class=\"home-btn\" href=\"/login\"> Login </a><a class=\"home-btn\" href=\"/register\"> Join Us </a><a class=\"home-btn\" href=\"#\"> How To use This Course </a></div>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome! When you join our INCLUDE learning community, you will be connecting with other CBR and development professionals who are committed to community-based development that is truly inclusive.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As an INCLUDE community member, you will be able to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong><em>Learn</em></strong>&nbsp;about Community-based Rehabilitation (CBR) as an inclusive development strategy to realize the rights of people with disabilities at the community level</li><li><strong><em>Discover</em></strong>&nbsp;how other programmes are putting CBRs inclusive development strategy into action</li><li><strong><em>Create</em></strong>&nbsp;your own action plan for inclusive development</li><li><strong><em>Share</em></strong>&nbsp;experiences, thoughts and ideas with a community of other dedicated individuals working in CBR</li><li><strong><em>Reflect</em></strong>&nbsp;on your own experiences and beliefs about inclusive development</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Welcome to the INCLUDE learning community!','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2019-05-25 15:17:48','2019-05-25 15:17:48','',2,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/25/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(235,1,'2019-05-25 19:28:44','2019-05-25 19:28:44','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Introduction to management</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nBefore you begin viewing this module, we suggest that you take a few moments to reflect on your thoughts about what is required to manage CBR activities that are inclusive, highly participatory and sustainable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\".cbr-matrix\">CBR Matrix</a>, created as part of the CBR Guidelines, has a set of common organizing principles for community-based rehabilitation, which are introduced in this module.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recognized and expected that each CBR activity is unique and will need to make important decisions based on the human and economic resources available, as well as the economic, political and cultural environment in which the programme must operate. These decisions include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>which components of the CBR Matrix will need to be implemented to address the needs, priorities and resources of the communities being served?</li>\r\n 	<li>how will the programme need to be adapted to satisfy the cultural values and expectations of the different groups and communities being served?</li>\r\n 	<li>how can the programme be most effectively structured and managed?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','Introduction','','publish','closed','closed','','introduction-to-management','','','2019-05-30 08:09:52','2019-05-30 08:09:52','',178,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=235',1,'modules','',0),(236,1,'2019-05-25 19:32:08','2019-05-25 19:32:08','<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-237\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/management_new_0-300x242.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"242\" />\r\n\r\n<p>A well-managed CBR activity:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>implements the CBR components that best match the needs, priorities and resources of the community;</li>\r\n 	<li>is inclusive of all key community stakeholders, especially people with disabilities, their family members and organizations that represent them; and</li>\r\n 	<li>ensures equal treatment by implementing the rights in the Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities (CRPD).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','Preamble','','publish','closed','closed','','preamble','','','2019-05-30 07:12:23','2019-05-30 07:12:23','',178,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=236',2,'modules','',0),(237,1,'2019-05-25 19:32:01','2019-05-25 19:32:01','','management_new_0','','inherit','open','closed','','management_new_0','','','2019-05-25 19:32:01','2019-05-25 19:32:01','',236,'http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/management_new_0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(238,1,'2019-05-25 19:35:34','2019-05-25 19:35:34','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Creating a programme that fits your unique situation</h3>\r\n<p>Every CBR activity is unique; and each programme needs to be designed, structured and managed to respond effectively to a wide range of influences  physical, socioeconomic, cultural and political.</p>','Introduction','','publish','closed','closed','','introduction','','','2019-05-30 07:13:04','2019-05-30 07:13:04','',236,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=238',0,'modules','',0),(240,1,'2019-05-25 19:37:30','2019-05-25 19:37:30','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Desirable outcomes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>People with disabilities</strong>are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>actively and meaningfully involved in the management of CBR.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>CBR activities:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>are based on a thorough analysis of the needs of all people with disabilities, including those most at risk of exclusion;</li>\r\n 	<li>mobilize and coordinate relevant stakeholders;</li>\r\n 	<li>build a sense of joint ownership among all stakeholders in support of programme sustainability;</li>\r\n 	<li>effectively contribute at an affordable cost to building inclusive communities and realizing the rights of all community members, including persons with disabilities; and</li>\r\n 	<li>develop the capacities of CBR staff to ensure continual quality improvement.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Within the<strong>community</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>decision-makers will put in place policies that implement the CRPD and budget for the inclusion of people with disabilities; and</li>\r\n 	<li>service providers will deliver services that are accessible and inclusive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','Desirable outcomes','','publish','closed','closed','','desirable-outcomes','','','2019-05-30 08:03:00','2019-05-30 08:03:00','',236,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=240',0,'modules','',0),(241,1,'2019-05-25 19:39:51','2019-05-25 19:39:51','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Key concepts</h3>\r\n<p>Here are some of the most important ideas you need to understand in order to manage a CBR programme effectively.\r\n</p>\r\n<em>Use your mouse or keyboard to expand each of the headings below.</em>','Key concepts','','publish','closed','closed','','key-concepts','','','2019-05-30 08:00:58','2019-05-30 08:00:58','',236,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=241',0,'modules','',0),(242,1,'2019-05-25 19:41:17','2019-05-25 19:41:17','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Elements in this module</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Management module is made up of the following elements.</p>\r\n\r\n<em>Use your mouse or keyboard to expand each of the headings below.</em>\r\n\r\n\r\n','Elements in this module','','publish','closed','closed','','elements-in-this-module','','','2019-05-30 08:28:00','2019-05-30 08:28:00','',236,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=242',0,'modules','',0),(243,1,'2019-05-25 19:42:53','2019-05-25 19:42:53','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Management structures</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In this section you will learn about the several ways that CBR can be structured</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"field-item even\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-237\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/management_new_0-300x242.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"242\" /></h3>\r\n','Management structures','','publish','closed','closed','','management-structures','','','2019-05-30 08:30:38','2019-05-30 08:30:38','',178,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=243',3,'modules','',0),(244,1,'2019-05-25 19:47:32','2019-05-25 19:47:32','<h3 class=\"page-header\">Introduction to management structures</h3>\r\n<p>Each CBR programme must decide how to manage itself. It is not possible to provide one overall management structure that can be used in every instance.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe management structure that each programme ultimately implements will be determined in large part by the political, funding and social environment in which the programme must operate.\r\n</p>\r\n','Introduction to management structures','','publish','closed','closed','','introduction-to-management-structures','','','2019-05-30 08:43:22','2019-05-30 08:43:22','',243,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=modules&#038;p=244',0,'modules','',0),(248,1,'2019-05-26 10:41:52','2019-05-26 10:41:52','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>INCLUDE: A learning resource for managers of CBR and other development programmes</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">INCLUDE contains 8 modules of information that will help you learn about CBR and how to implement inclusive development principles in your programme.&nbsp;<em>To view any of the modules (shown below), select its picture.</em></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"><button class=\"learn-more ml-learn\">How to use this course</button></div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;The modules can be viewed in any order; however we recommend that you start with the Introduction module.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Module Library','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-autosave-v1','','','2019-05-26 10:41:52','2019-05-26 10:41:52','',168,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/26/168-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(249,1,'2019-05-26 10:42:31','2019-05-26 10:42:31',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','249','','','2019-06-21 05:41:05','2019-06-21 05:41:05','',0,'http://include.xyz/?p=249',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(250,1,'2019-05-27 06:33:14','2019-05-27 06:33:14','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Build capacity of individuals and families</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR personnel need to work closely with people with disabilities and their family members to ensure that those who need assistive devices get the maximum benefit from them.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following checklist to ensure that CBR workers have the skills they need to provide the necessary support for people who need assistive devices. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR personnel should possess the skills needed to support people with disabilities and their family members as they select and use assistive devices. Those who require assistive devices must be able to do the following.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Understand the different types of assistive devices and how these can assist individuals to achieve independence and participation\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Consider engaging members of the community who are using assistive devices to explain their use and value</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Participate in decision-making regarding the selection and design of assistive devices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Providing opportunities for people to see and try assistive devices will assist them in making informed decisions\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Use their assistive devices properly and safely to achieve optimum function\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Perform repairs and maintenance to ensure long-term use\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide feedback to referral services about any difficulties experienced so that adjustments can be made and different options considered\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Prevent secondary complications that may arise from using the devices\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Note:</b> Self-help groups enable people to share valuable information, experiences and skills like the ones mentioned above. These groups can be particularly beneficial when someone has limited access to rehabilitation personnel.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before send