:52','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"271\" title=\"Lobby and advocate for inclusion\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-29 10:37:52','2019-05-29 10:37:52','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/29/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(273,1,'2019-05-29 10:43:49','2019-05-29 10:43:49','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Prepare for emergency, conflict and refugee situations</b></h5>\r\n<p>The well-being of the young child is crucial in any emergency, conflict or natural disaster. CBR can help to ensure that there are inclusive child-friendly spaces and opportunities for play activities; this often means interacting with United Nations organizations as well as nongovernmental organizations and government services.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify resources</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify the United Nations organizations, non-governmental organizations, and government services that could help in a time of crisis:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Organization</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Area of focus</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>2. Network and prepare for future emergency</b></p>\r\n<p>Next, take steps to connect and work with these organizations to prepare for situations of emergency. In particular, work with these partners to think about and prepare for ways to sustain early childhood education during these crises. For more information about preparing for and responding to humanitarian crises, see the see the Humanitarian Crises portion of the Supplementary module.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date form