09:05','2019-06-03 06:09:05','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Support the child with disability</b></h5>\r\n<p>Many children with disabilities are prevented from accessing primary education because of poor health status and environmental barriers. Improvements in health and physical access can be achieved with appropriate medical care, rehabilitation and assistive devices. CBR should ensure that children with disabilities can access these services to ensure that they are able to get out of their house, reach school and access primary education.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Are there any children with disabilities in your community that your programme can support in specific ways? Use the chart below to identify the needs of the children in your community. In order to assess their needs, CBR personnel should talk with their parents and teachers, and the child directly. Think about some of the examples listed earlier, such as transportation, medical care, rehabilitation and assistive devices.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Children in your community</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Possible barriers</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Possible solutions</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[