erit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-06-13 09:54:30','2019-06-13 09:54:30','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/06/13/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(344,1,'2019-06-13 10:33:34','2019-06-13 10:33:34','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Help to create an inclusive learning environment</b></h5>\r\n<p>While many of the activities that can be used to promote inclusiveness in secondary and higher education are similar to those used in primary education, there are some specific things to consider when supporting secondary and higher education.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Environment and location</b></p>\r\n<p>Secondary and higher educational establishments are often bigger than primary schools and draw students from large areas. Because of this, travel between classrooms can be an issue, as well as accessibility within classrooms like laboratories or computer rooms.</p>\r\n<p>To address these issues, CBR can:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Negotiate with school authorities to change the locations of classes\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><ul><li>Move some classes to the ground floor\r\n</li></ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Support students with disabilities in finding creative solutions to accessibility issues\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Work together with students to identify specific accessibility issues that they face. Then look for and create solutions by working with others in the community, including:\r\n<ul><li>Other students, both with and without disabilities</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>School staff</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Local government</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that girls and young women are able to access private and hygienic water and sanitation facilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Assess the situation for girls and young women in the local secondary and higher education centres in your community, and take steps to work with staff and officials to make them more safe and accessible if needed. List each water/sanitation facility in a separate row in this table:\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>School</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Level of privacy</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Hygiene level</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Actions to take</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Curriculum and teaching methods</p>\r\n<p>Teachers need training and support, and a supportive environment where they can discuss their successes and challenges in educating students with disabilities. CBR should work together with teachers and others in the education sector to provide advice and resource materials where possible. Some suggested activities are listed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Help to adapt and develop curricula to make them relevant and accessible\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Involve people with disabilities in a review process to identify needed adaptations</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Advise on classroom organization\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some areas of advice you could provide:[textarea textarea-180 id:textarea class:textarea2 cols:60 rows:4]\r\n<b>Examples:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Seating</li>\r\n<li>Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Positioning of students</li>\r\n<li>Encourage group-work and team-teaching</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Help:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Create accessible formats and communication systems</li>\r\n<li>Make sure that assistive devices and services are available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What are some assistive devices and services that could meet the needs of the students in the community? Examples include:\r\nExamples include:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Large-print text</li>\r\n<li>Braille</li>\r\n<li>Signboards</li>\r\n<li>Sign interpretation</li>\r\n<li>Tapes</li>\r\n<li>Audio facilities</li>\r\n<li>Scribes</li>\r\n<li>Translation</li>\r\n[textarea textarea-180 id:textarea class:textarea2 cols:60 rows:4]\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more information, see the <a href=\"/health/664/assistive-devices\">Assistive Devices</a> portion of the Health module.\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage flexible schedules so that curricula can be completed over a longer duration of time\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some areas of advice you could provide:[textarea textarea-180 id:textarea class:textarea2 cols:60 rows:4]\r\n<b>Examples:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Allow more time to complete activities</li>\r\n<li>Provide opportunities for learning at different times</li>\r\n<li>Provide opportunities to learn in modules</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that students with disabilities are involved in discussions about their learning, support requirements and progress\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify some areas of advice you could provide:[textarea textarea-180 id:textarea class:textarea2 cols:60 rows:4]\r\n<b>Note:</b>In addition to involving students in conversations about their own learning, also remember to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Seek and respond to their opinions about how and what they learn</li>\r\n<li>Embrace their highest potential by providing counseling and careers advice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>3. Examination and assessment</b>\r\n<p>Examination and assessment systems can be made more flexible and adapted to meet the needs of all students. This may include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Allowing for additional time during testing</li>\r\n<li>Adjusting the environment with appropriate lighting or physical supports</li>\r\n<li>Providing assistive devices or services like Braille, scribes, or translation</li></ul>\r\n<p>What are some specific adaptations that could be useful for the students in your community?</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Student</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Specific needs</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Adaptations to consider</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>4. Information and communications technology</b>\r\n<p>At the higher education level in particular, computer technology can offer a creative and effective means of learning and accessing the curriculum. CBR can explore the possibility of grants or funding from local communities, businesses, government and international agencies, for providing computers, preferably with an Internet connection, for students with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p>Do some research about the potential sources of funding and resources for your community. Are there any currently existing grants or resource pools?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Existing sources of funding or resources</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Organization and contact information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>If there are no (or not enough) funding options, what organizations could your programme communicate with to discuss the possibility of creating additional such programmes?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Possible organizations to talk with</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Possible resources</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[text text-148 id:text3 class:text3 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>5. Peer support and role-models</b>\r\n<p>Many students may not have studied alongside students with disabilities before. As a result, attitudes and reactions can vary. Some classmates can be helpful and mature, while others may behave in ways that exclude students with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p>To support students with disabilities, your organisation can:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage schools to sensitize students, preferably with leadership from an adult with a disability\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify adults in the school, community, or your organisation who could take the lead in sensitizing students:\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage the development of policies and procedures to prevent discrimination, bullying and teasing by both classmates and teachers\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">What kinds of policies are already in place? Are there any changes that could be made to those policies?\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Existing policy</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible changes</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:1]</d