1 \"Encourage the community and school authorities to organize transport facilities  this may require requesting financial assistance from credit groups and practical support from self-help/self-advocacy groups\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Examples:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Guides</li>\r\n<li>Readers</li>\r\n<li>Writers</li>\r\n<li>Interpreters</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Itinerant teachers who make regular visits to schools to provide advice and support\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Additional support outside the mainstream school\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples of types of support to provide:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer skills</li>\r\n<li>School staff</li>\r\n<li>Local government</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou