>\r\n<p>Often, students with disabilities need to move away from their communities to complete higher education. This can make transitional periods more difficult, and many find adjustment very challenging without the support of their families and communities.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Secondary and higher education is at the centre of change for many individuals and families. While the transition can be difficult for anyone, it can be especially difficult for people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p>CBR can work with students, families, community members and educational institutions to ensure supportive links are created and maintained throughout transitional periods.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Transition</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible support(s)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Primary to secondary</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-218 id:textarea11 class:textarea112 cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Secondary to tertiary</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-218 id:textarea11 class:textarea112 cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Tertiary to sustainable livelihood</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-218 id:textarea11 class:textarea112 cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomox