class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-897 id:text11 class:text12 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Promote accessibility and inclusiveness</b>\r\n<p>Contact each of the institutions listed above and do the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Encourage the enrolment of people with disabilities in all types of programmes\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that the educational environment is welcoming to students with disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Offer to help provide awareness-raising training for staff and students</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that all teaching is conducted in accessible locations\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Examples:</b>Educational facilities must be:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Accessible to students with physical disabilities</li>\r\n<li>Located close enough so students with disabilities do not have difficulty traveling to school</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-390 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Work together with non-formal education facilitators, students with disabilities and their families to ensure that all teaching materials are available in accessible formats\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Examples:</b>Materials should be provided in large print, Braille and audio\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Help make existing non-formal programmes inclusive','','publish','closed','closed','','help-make-existing-non-formal-programmes-inclusive','','','2019-07-04 13:09:31','2019-07-04 13:09:31','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=350',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(351,1,'2019-06-14 06:21:55','2019-06-14 06:21:55','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"350\" title=\"Help make existing non-formal programmes inclusive\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-06-14 06:21:55','2019-06-14 06:21:55','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/06/14/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(353,1,'2019-06-14 07:14:55','2019-06-14 07:14:55','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Support home-based learning</b></h5>\r\n<p>Home-based learning can be supplementary, preparatory or an alternative to formal education. It can be relevant for students with extensive needs, for whom the priority is to learn basic daily living skills, basic communication and basic functioning. CBR personnel can work closely with family members, teachers and students, carry out home visits on a regular basis and work with the entire family to ensure successful home-based learning.</p>\r\n<p>Home-based learning, as part of a comprehensive strategy, is effective. However, when it operates in isolation, home-based learning can contribute to exclusion and isolation of children with disabilities, despite working closely with family members and sometimes with teachers.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Assess the situation</b></p>\r\n<p>First, assess the situation for each of the families who have children with disabilities in your community. This chart contains examples as a starting point for you to gauge the level of inclusion and exclusion experienced by each child and family.</p>\r\n<p>Keep in mind that there may be more areas for your organisation to assess than what this chart covers. The chart contains additional space for you to include additional criteria.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2  w-50\"><strong>Indications of inclusion</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Indications of exclusion</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Your organisation has supported family and child from birth\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Family is stigmatized because of the child\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Volunteers and other children help teach the child activities of daily living in his/ her own home\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Older sibling or siblings drop out of school to care for the child\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Child is taken out and involved in local activities, religious and social events\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Neighbours and other children avoid visiting and fear the child\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Teacher visits family and develops appropriate learning goals together with CBR personnel and family\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Child is kept indoors most of the time\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Child attends playgroup at appropriate age\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Family spends money on seeking cures that do not work\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"District education team includes this child in its planning, provision and resource allocation\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Parent or parents leave the family due to shame or stigma\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Parent or parents are active members of the local parent/disabled peoples group, and are able to plan/lobby for the childs future\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Parent or parents neglect/abuse the child\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Siblings are able to get married or get jobs without fear of stigma\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1 \"Siblings cannot get married or get jobs due to stigma\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-606 id:checkbox class:checkbox1][text text-507 id:text1 class:text1]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>2. Identify solutions</b>\r\n<p>Remember that this assessment is only an indicator, and that it is important to assess the complete situation for each family. However, the assessment can help your organisation identify some areas to help the family.</p>\r\n<p>What are some specific actions your organisation can take to help the family? Be sure to collaborate with the family members to agree on appropriate and helpful actions.</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-917 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:120 rows:5]\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Support home-based learning','','publish','closed','closed','','ensure-the-curriculum-is-practical-and-relevant','','','2019-07-04 13:23:08','2019-07-04 13:23:08','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=353',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(354,1,'20