rt strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Assess the existing situation at the community-based day centres in your area. What sorts of activities do children participate in at the centre? Are the activities age-appropriate for the children? Are children with disabilities included?</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Day centre name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Age of children</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Activities</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Are activities age-appropriate?</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Are children with disabilities included?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-119 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:21 