formal or continuing education, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Inability to meet entry qualifications</li>\r\n<li>Inaccessibility of buildings</li>\r\n<li>Inability to pay fees</li>\r\n<li>Unwillingness of the institution to accept a learner with a disability</li>\r\n<li>Having to work during school hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>CBR can identify and create opportunities for adult literacy and adult education through open schooling within the wider community.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>1. Programme support</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify existing open schools and adult literacy programmes in your community. Assess each one: Do they currently include adults with disabilities? Are their teaching materials and communication methods appropriate and accessible?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Programme name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Inclusive of adults with disabilities (Y/N)\r\n</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Teaching material is accessible (Y/N)\r\n</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Communication methods are accessible (Y/N)\r\n</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>If any of the programmes listed are not inclusive or accessible, work with the leaders and staff of the programme to make the appropriate changes to do so. Consider providing the following to help:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Training sessions about disability</li>\r\n<li>Ideas about how to support people with disabilities</li>\r\n<li>Ways to create accessible accommodations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[textarea textarea-923 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:3]\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><b>2. Individualized support</b></p>\r\n<p>Adults with disabilities may face a variety of obstacles to pursuing education. Identify the specific obstacles that affect each adult with disabilities who wishes to pursue education in your community, and work with them to develop solutions for overcoming those obstacles.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Obstacles</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Strengths</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Solutions</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class: