369,1,'2019-06-17 09:35:54','2019-06-17 09:35:54','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"368\" title=\"Facilitate learning for individuals and groups with particular needs\"]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-06-17 09:35:54','2019-06-17 09:35:54','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/06/17/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(370,1,'2019-06-17 12:11:43','2019-06-17 12:11:43','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Ensure opportunities for learning life and survival skills</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR programmes can work with organizations and community groups to provide opportunities for youth and adults with disabilities to develop the skills required for daily life and participation in society.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>As you plan your organisations next steps in this area, remember that its better to identify existing education programmes and work to make them inclusive rather than set up parallel programmes.</p>\r\n<p>Identify some of the skills that people with disabilities in your community may need help and training to develop. Some examples may include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Self-care</li>\r\n<li>Transport</li>\r\n<li>Shopping</li>\r\n<li>Appropriate social behaviour</li>\r\n<li>Assertiveness and self-esteem</li>\r\n<li>Sexuality</li>\r\n<li>Marriage and parenting</li>\r\n<li>HIV/AIDS awareness</li>\r\n<li>Maintaining health and well-being</li>\r\n<li>Financial management</li>\r\n<li>Citizenship and political participation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\