div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-838 id:cf-321-1 class:cf-321-1 \"Help community members meet and interact with people with disabilities, particularly in educational settings\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify existing settings where members of the community can interact with people with disabilities, and focus especially on educational settings if possible. Some examples may include:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Formal and non-formal classes</li>\r\n<li>Religious education settings</li>\r\n<li>Workforce training settings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Setting</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Time/Date</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Types of activities</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2 class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 ve