tuation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Secondary schools sometimes offer vocational education courses, as well as vocational assessment and career guidance and counselling. Students with disabilities should have an opportunity to enrol in such vocational courses and benefit from career guidance services. They should also have an opportunity to benefit from transition programmes for youth from school to work.</p>\r\n<p>Some ways in which your organization can help students with disabilities take advantage of such services are show below.</p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify vocational training opportunities</b></p>\r\n<b>Secondary schools</b>\r\n<p>Identify secondary schools that offer vocational education courses and related support services in the communities your organization serves.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Secondary school name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Type(s) of training provided</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Barrier(s) to the participation<br>of students with disabilities</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact person</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-511 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100 rows:3]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2