rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Meet with each individual with disability and his or her family to discuss their situation\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Be sure to discuss:\r\n<ul><li>The interests of the individual with disability, whether they have existing skills, and what family support is already available\r\n</li></ul></div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Meet with each individual with disability and his or her family to discuss their situation\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Suggest products or services that could be produced or provided to meet local demand\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Products or services to suggest:\r\n[textarea textarea-130 id:textarea class:textarea12 rows:3]</div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>If a <b>mainstream training programme</b> is the best solution:</em>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Provide the individual with disability with the support needed to gain access to the programme\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Recommended training programme:\r\n[textarea textarea-130 id:textarea class:textarea12 rows:3]</div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Follow up with the training programme and student\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Be sure to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ensure that learning and training are taking place, and</li>\r\n<li>Help overcome any problems that may arise</li>\r\n</ul></div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>If an <b>apprenticeship</b> is the best solution:</em>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Identify a local person who is already engaged in that occupation or in providing training, and encourage them to take on an apprentice who has a disability\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Recommended mentor:\r\n[textarea textarea-130 id:textarea class:textarea12 rows:3]</div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Identify and find solutions to potential obstacles to the individual becoming an apprentice\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Be sure to consider:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cost</li>\r\n<li>Access</li>\r\n<li>Mobility</li>\r\n<li>Other required support (e.g. transport, sign language interpreter, assistive devices)</li>\r\n</ul></div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"As necessary, provide material support to the master trainer\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-323 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Follow up with the master trainer and apprentice\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Be sure to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ensure that learning and training are taking place, and</li>\r\n<li>Help overcome any problems that may arise</li>\r\n</ul></div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Following <b>successful completion</b> of the training:</em>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-847 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Provide assistance to the trainee to start his/her activity\"]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div> \r\n</div> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button 