choice of what sort of business activity an individual with disability will engage in is the decision of the individual and should be based upon his or her interests, skills and resources.</p>\r\n<p><em>CBR staff members can use the following planning tool to help individuals select the business activity that best matches their situation. Try answering the questions now for a particular individual you have in mind. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify interests</b></p>\r\n<p>Help the individual with disability identify his or her interests.</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-934 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:5]\r\n<p><b>2. Identify skills and resources</b></p>\r\n<p>Help the individual identify skills and resources he or she possesses that could be used to generate an income.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">Skills:</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">Resources:</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-934 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100  rows:5]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-934 id:textarea class:textarea12 class:w-100  rows:5]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<b>3. Identify sources of support</b>\r\n<p>Identify sources of support available from family members.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Family member</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Support</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 w-50\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1  class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265