> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Medical and vocational rehabilitation centres</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Location</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact Information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Financial services</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Location</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact Information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1 class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Link individuals with the appropriate opportunities</b>\r\n<p>After collecting background information about the employment and support opportunities available to people with disabilities, CBR needs to work directly with individuals to determine their interests, needs and capabilities, and to link each individual with the employment opportunities and support services that will best match their situation.</p>\r\n<b>Assess the job seekers interests and capabilities</b>\r\n<p>Prior to seeking a job, it is important for each job seeker to identify what he or she wants to do. CBR should help each individual assess his or her interests and goals, skills, talents, motivation and forms of support . Steps to help do this are:</p>\r\n<b>1. Talk with each individual to determine their:</b>\r\n<p>Education:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:4]\r\n<p>Training:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:4]\r\n<p>Work history:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:4]\r\n<p>Day-to-day activities:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:4]\r\n<p>Goals and aspirations:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:4]\r\n\r\n<b>2. Observe each individual performing their daily chores or on a job try-out</b>\r\n<p>Notes:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:5]\r\n<b>Assess potential support needs</b>\r\n<p>It is important to understand how a persons disabilities may impact him or her in the workplace. To do this, CBR personnel can:</p>\r\n<b>1. Ask the person with disabilities directly about his/her needs</b>\r\n<p>Notes:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:5]\r\n<b>2. Observe the individual in work or daily living activities</b>\r\n<p>Notes:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:5]\r\n<b>3. From the information collected, identify required support or adaptations the person may need in the work environment.</b>\r\n<p>Support or adaptations required:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-744 id:textarea class:textarea12 cols:135 rows:5]\r\n<b>Examples:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Extra time to do a job</li>\r\n<li>An interpreter</li>\r\n<li>Special equipment, or</li>\r\n<li>Assistance with transport</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Help to match the person to the job</b>\r\n<p>In job seeking, a vital part of supporting people with disabilities to find a job is to make a good match between their skills, talents, potential support needs in the workplace and the requirements of the job.</p>\r\n<p>To find a good match, it may be necessary to carry out a job or work analysis for each employment opportunity. To do this, analyze the existing job to assess:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"What the worker does\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"How the work is done\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Where it is done\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"The conditions under which it is done, and\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"What skills and abilities are required\"]\r\n<b>Provide training to develop job-seeking skills</b>\r\n<p>Many job seekers with disabilities are able to look for their own jobs. However, some can benefit from training to help them develop job-seeking skills. If necessary, provide individuals with training in how to:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Write a curriculum vitae\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Look for job opportunities (in the newspapers, through family members and other contacts)\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Fill in an application form\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Develop telephone or letter-writing skills\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Perform well in a job interview\"]\r\n<b>Provide support</b>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Link individuals with the support services (identified above) best suited to their situations\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-593 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"If needed, provide job seekers with access to the facilities they will need to look for employment, for example:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A telephone</li>\r\n<li>A computer</li>\r\n<li>A desk</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Enable and assist people with disabilities to find jobs','','publish','closed','closed','','enable-and-assist-people-with-disabilities-to-find-jobs','','','2019-07-04 12:56:33','2019-07-04 12:56:33','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=407',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(408,1,'2019-06-20 09:01:11','2019-06-20 09:01:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or