ref=\"#v-pills-474\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-474\" aria-selected=\"true\">Assist people with disabilities to develop individual support plans</a>\n\n  <a class=\"nav-link\" id=\"v-pills-477-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-477\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-477\" aria-selected=\"true\">Support training opportunities</a>\n\n <a class=\"nav-link\" id=\"v-pills-485-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-485\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-485\" aria-selected=\"true\">Ensure family members are supported in their roles as personal assistants</a>\n\n<a class=\"nav-link\" id=\"v-pills-488-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-488\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-488\" aria-selected=\"true\">Prepare for and manage crisis situations</a>\n\n<a class=\"nav-link\" id=\"v-pills-491-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-491\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-491\" aria-selected=\"true\">Encourage a move away from institutional care</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n\n  <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-474\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-474-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"474\" title=\"Assist people with disabilities to develop individual support plans\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show\" id=\"v-pills-477\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-477-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"477\" title=\"Support training opportunities\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show\" id=\"v-pills-485\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-485-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"485\" title=\"Ensure family members are supported in their roles as personal assistants\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show\" id=\"v-pills-488\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-488-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"488\" title=\"Prepare for and manage crisis situations\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show\" id=\"v-pills-491\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-491-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"491\" title=\"Encourage a move away from institutional care\"]</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-01 06:26:34','2019-07-01 06:26:34','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/01/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(497,1,'2019-07-02 06:12:07','2019-07-02 06:12:07','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination</b></h4>\r\n<p>People with disabilities often face negative attitudes, perceptions and practices against them in their communities. CBR can help to change this.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Work with the following groups to challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination in the communities your programme serves.</p>\r\n<p><b>Media groups</b></p>\r\n<p>Work with the local media groups to promote positive images of people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<b>1. Assess the current situation</b>\r\n<p>Start by assessing the current images of people with disabilities in the local media. Are people with disabilities shown? If so, what types of roles or characteristics are depicted? What needs to be addressed?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Type of media (print, video, etc.)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Are people with disabilities shown? (Y/N)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Roles and characteristics depicted</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Area(s) that need to be addressed</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea tom_r1c1 id:140-1 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea apwd_r1c3 id:140-3 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea racd_r1c4 id:140-4 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea atnb_r1c5 id:140-5 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea tom_r2c1 id:140-6 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea ci_r2c2  id:140-7 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea apwd_r2c3 id:140-8 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea racd_r2c4 id:140-9 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea atnb_r2c5 id:140-10 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea tom_r3c1 id:cf-140-11 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-12 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea apwd_r3c3 id:cf-140-13 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea racd_r3c4 id:cf-140-14 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea atnb_r3c5 id:cf-140-15 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea tom_r4c1 id:cf-140-16 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-17 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea apwd_r4c3 id:cf-140-18 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea racd_r4c4 id:cf-140-19 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea atnb_r4c5 id:cf-140-20 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea tom_r5c1 id:cf-140-21 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-22 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea apwd_r5c3 id:cf-140-23 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea racd_r5c4 id:cf-140-24 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[textarea atnb_r5c5 id:cf-140-25 class:textarea rows:3 cols:15]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Next, identify people with disabilities in your community who might be willing and able to work with your organisation and the media groups to promote positive images of disability.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r5c1 id:cf-140-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Promote positive images of disability</b>\r\n<p>Work together with the media groups and people with disabilities listed above to promote positive images of disability.</p>\r\n<p>Characteristics to promote</p>\r\n<p>First, identify the positive characteristics you believe are important to promote.</p>\r\n<b>Characteristics to promote</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cop_r1 id:cf-140-36 class:text class:w-100]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cop_r2 id:cf-140-37 class:text class:w-100]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cop_r3 id:cf-140-38 class:text class:w-100]\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cop_r4 id:cf-140-39 class:text class:w-100]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text cop_r5 id:cf-140-40 class:text class:w-100]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Potential role-models</p>\r\n<p>Next, identify individuals with disabilities in the communities you serve who could serve as positive role-models.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-41 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-44 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-46 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r4c2 id:cf-140-47 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-48 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n_r5c2 id:cf-140-49 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-50 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Health professionals</p>\r\n<p>Work with local and regional health professionals to ensure that sexual and reproductive health services are accessible to people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p>Identify sexual and reproductive health services such as family planning services. Assess the accessibility and inclusiveness of each of these services, and identify ways in which your organisation can support them to become more accessible and inclusive.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n1_r1c1 id:cf-140-51 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci1_r1c2 id:cf-140-52 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n1_r2c1 id:cf-140-53 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci1_r2c2 id:cf-140-54 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n1_r3c1 id:cf-140-55 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci1_r3c2 id:cf-140-56 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n1_r4c1 id:cf-140-57 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci1_r4c2 id:cf-140-58 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text n1_r5c1 id:cf-140-59 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text ci1_r5c2 id:cf-140-60 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Now, work with the health professionals identified above, including people with disabilities in your training and awareness activities as much as possible.</p>\r\n<b>Community leaders</b>\r\n<p>Work with leaders in the community and encourage them to increase awareness, acceptance and support of people with disabilities within the community.</p>\r\n<b>1. Identify community leaders</b>\r\n<p>Identify community leaders with whom your organisation can work.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Leaders name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Organization (e.g. local church, education board)\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Sphere of influence (e.g. parents of school-age children, elderly)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea ln_r1c1 id:cf-140-61 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea olc_r1c2 id:cf-140-62 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea soi_r1c3 id:cf-140-63 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea ci_r1c4 id:cf-140-64 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea ln_r2c1 id:cf-140-65 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea olc_r2c2 id:cf-140-66 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea soi_r2c3 id:cf-140-67 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea ci_r2c4 id:cf-140-68 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea ln_r3c1 id:cf-140-69 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea olc_r3c2 id:cf-140-70 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[textarea soi_r3c3 id:cf-140-71 class:textarea rows:3 cols:19]</di