heck1 id:cf-519-3 class:checkbox \"Make sure that CBR personnel know how to access appropriate legal advice and support for people with disabilities\"]</div>\r\nIdentify services or programmes that can provide appropriate legal advice and support for people with disabilities. Work with these organizations to establish referral systems if necessary.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name of service or programme</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Services provided</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nosop_r1c1 id:cf-519-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea sp_r1c2 id:cf-519-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciiii_r1c3 id:cf-519-6 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nosop_r2c1 id:cf-519-7 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea sp_r2c2 id:cf-519-8 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciiii_r2c3 id:cf-519-9 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nosop_r3c1 id:cf-519-10 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea sp_r3c2 id:cf-519-11 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciiii_r3c3 id:cf-520-12 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nosop_r4c1 id:cf-519-13 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea sp_r4c2 id:cf-519-14 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciiii_r4c3 id:cf-519-15 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox rawc_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Raise awareness within communities about violence and disability and about actions that can be taken to protect people with disabilities.\"]</div>\r\n\r\nIdentify organizations (e.g. local disabled peoples organizations, violence prevention networks) with which your organisation can work to disseminate information.\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Organization name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Areas of focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea on_r1c1 id:cf-519-17 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea aof_r1c2 id:cf-519-18 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea cisp_r1c3 id:cf-519-19 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea on_r2c1 id:cf-519-20 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea aof_r2c2 id:cf-519-21 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea cisp_r2c3 id:cf-519-22 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea on_r3c1 id:cf-519-23 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea aof_r3c2 id:cf-519-24 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea cisp_r3c3 id:cf-519-25 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea on_r4c1 id:cf-519-26 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea aof_r4c2 id:cf-519-27 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea cisp_r4c3 id:cf-519-28 class:textarea cols:12 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox elwrs_check1 id:cf-519-29 class:checkbox \"Establish links with relevant stakeholders and talk to them about their role in protecting people with disabilities from violence\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Examples of relevant stakeholders include:\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Families</li>\r\n		<li>Disabled peoples organizations</li>\r\n		<li>Health-care personnel</li>\r\n		<li>Education personnel</li>\r\n		<li>Law enforcement officers</li>\r\n		<li>Community leaders</li>\r\n		<li>Local authorities</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox dpws_check1 id:cf-519-30 class:checkbox \"Develop procedures with stakeholders that enable people with disabilities to report episodes of violence in confidence\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> If confidential procedures already exist, assess them and make any changes needed to ensure they are accessible to people with disabilities.</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox piavt_check1 id:cf-519-31 class:checkbox \"Provide information about violence to people with disabilities, including how they can report episodes of violence confidentially\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b>  Train people with disabilities on how they can communicate with the stakeholders mentioned above.</div></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox epwdh_check1 id:cf-519-32 class:checkbox \"Ensure people with disabilities have opportunities to participate in community life to increase their self-esteem and confidence, and develop social networks that will protect them from violence.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Brainstorm some community events that can include people with disabilities.\r\n<b>Potential community events</b>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea pce_r1c1 id:cf-519-33 class:textarea cols:45 rows:2]</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea pce_r2c1 id:cf-519-34 class:textarea cols:45 rows:2]</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea pce_r3c1 id:cf-519-35 class:textarea cols:45 rows:2]</div></div>\r\nIdentify advocates or mentors who can buddy with people with disabilities as they begin to participate in community life.\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Potential advocate or mentor</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea poam_r1c1 id:cf-519-36 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciap_r1c2 id:cf-519-37 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea poam_r2c1 id:cf-519-38 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea ciap_r2c2 id:cf-519-39 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n</