lish','closed','closed','','help-to-prevent-violence','','','2019-07-09 05:08:09','2019-07-09 05:08:09','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=519',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(520,1,'2019-07-08 10:18:34','2019-07-08 10:18:34','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n  <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-497-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-497\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-497\" aria-selected=\"true\">Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination</a>\n \n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-517-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-517\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-517\" aria-selected=\"true\">Support people with limited social networks</a>\n \n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-519-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-519\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-519\" aria-selected=\"true\">Help to prevent violence</a>\n\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n\n  <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-497\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-497-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"497\" title=\"Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination\"]</div>\n\n <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-517\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-517-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"517\" title=\"Support people with limited social networks\"]</div>\n   \n <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-519\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-519-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"519\" title=\"Help to prevent violence\"]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-08 10:18:34','2019-07-08 10:18:34','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/08/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(521,1,'2019-07-08 11:25:24','2019-07-08 11:25:24','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Promote the use of culture and art for social change</b></h4>\r\n<p>Disability advocacy and awareness campaigns are often more effective when based on locally relevant cultural and artistic media. Because of this, CBR should use these media to achieve social change for disability.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR programmes can work with local artists and producers to organize drama, arts and music events that challenge disability stigma and discrimination in the community.</p>\r\n<p><b>Identify issues to address</b></p>\r\n<p>First, identify the types of stigma and discrimination that are present in the community:</p>\r\n[textarea tom_r2c1 id:140-6 class:textarea rows:4 cols:97]\r\n<b>Identify artists</b>\r\n<p>Next, identify artists in your community who may be willing and able to help address these issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Artist name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Medium (dance, music, etc.)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r5c1 id:cf-140-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Identify projects to promote social change</b>\r\n<p>Work with the artists listed above to identify ways they could use their skills such as drama, visual art, or music events to challenge stigma and discrimination.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTa