y be difficult at first for family members to identify their fears. Allow individuals enough time to process their fears on their own; but be sure to follow up with them. Encourage each family member to do his or her own reflection, and then share with one another.\r\n<p>It may be helpful to provide family members with the following chart to guide their individual reflection. When family members feel ready, it may be useful for CBR staff members to work with them to help generate ideas of how to challenge their fears.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>My fears or worries</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Why do I think this?</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>What are some things I can do about this?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r1c1 id:cf-519-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r1c2 id:cf-519-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r1c3 id:cf-519-6 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r2c1 id:cf-519-10 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r2c2 id:cf-519-11 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r2c3 id:cf-520-12 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea mfow_r3c1 id:cf-519-13 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wditt_r3c2 id:cf-519-14 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wastic_r3c3 id:cf-519-15 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox pfitw_check1 id:cf-519-16 class:checkbox \"Put families in touch with others who share similar experiences and concerns\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\nIdentify organizations (e.g. local disabled peoples organizations, violence prevention networks) with which your organisation can work to disseminate information.\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Family name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Experiences</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Concerns</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r1c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r1c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r1c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r2c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r2c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r2c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text fa_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text expc_r3c2 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text conc_r3c3 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTab