ve</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Promote connections</b></p>\r\n<p>Connect people with disabilities with groups and disabled peoples organizations where they can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Connect with people who share similar interests in culture and the arts</li>\r\n	<li>Develop the confidence to participate in a variety of arts-related activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Group type</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Area(s) of focus</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>Promote arts-related activities</b>\r\n<p>Work with artists and stakeholders to promote, develop and implement arts-related activities that will actively include people with disabilities and their families.</p>\r\n<b>1. Identify artists</b>\r\n<p>Identify artists with disabilities who have achieved recognition for their art and who may be willing and able to help develop and implement programme activities. Your programme can work with the artists in a number of different ways  for example, artists can serve as:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Speakers</li>\r\n    <li>Trainers</li>\r\n    <li>Role-models</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Artist name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Types of artwork</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Recognition attained</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Possible roles to play</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Note:</b> Be sure to consider and support people with disabilities who have developed new art forms such as e.g. silent theatre and who have created art forms that have been successfully adapted to reach wider audiences.\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>2. Identify stakeholders</b>\r\n<p>Identify stakeholders with whom your organisation could work to develop arts-related activities for people with disabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Stakeholder name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Arts-related interest(s)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>3. Identify activities</b>\r\n