e fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-497\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-497-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"497\" title=\"Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-528\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-528-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"528\" title=\"Encourage people with disabilities to participate\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-09 07:16:13','2019-07-09 07:16:13','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/09/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(530,1,'2019-07-09 13:58:53','2019-07-09 13:58:53','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Work with mainstream organizations and groups</b></h4>\r\n<p>Mainstream organizations that offer cultural and artistic programmes and activities may feel that they dont know how to include people with disabilities. CBR can help these organizations to be more inclusive and accessible to people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Increase accessibility and inclusion</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR can work with art and other organizations to help them make their facilities and programmes more accessible and inclusive of people with disabilities. Necessary accommodations may be physical such as modifying buildings to ensure physical access or informational such as producing information and promotional materials in accessible formats.</p>\r\n<p>Arts organizations</p>\r\n<p>Identify arts and cultural organizations whose facilities and programmes are not fully accessible and inclusive of people with disabilities. Arts-related buildings that may need modification include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Community halls</li>\r\n	<li>Places of worship</li>\r\n	<li>Cinemas</li>\r\n	<li>Tourist attractions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Organization name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Physical accommodations needed</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Informational accommodations needed</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Other accommodations needed</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r4c1 id:cf-140-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r5c1 id:cf-140-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r5c2 id:cf-140-35 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Womens groups</b>\r\n<p>Identify existing womens groups in your community and develop alliances with them to increase the inclusion of women with disabilities in mainstream cultural programmes. Assess each groups inclusiveness of women with disabilities. Where needed, work with group staff to help them understand disabilities and how they can be more accessible and inclusive.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r1c3 id:140-3 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r1c4 id:140-4 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r1c5 id:140-5 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r2c3 id:140-8 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r2c4 id:140-9 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r2c5 id:140-10 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea tom_r3c1 id:cf-140-11 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r3c4 id:cf-140-14 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r3c5 id:cf-140-15 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ci_r4c2 id:cf-140-17 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r4c4 id:cf-140-19 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r4c5 id:cf-140-20 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea apwd_r5c3 id:cf-140-23 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea racd_r5c4 id:cf-140-24 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea atnb_r5c5 id:cf-140-25 class:textarea rows:4 cols:28]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>Promote art education</b>\r\n<p>Encourage inclusive art education in early childhood and school settings so children with disabilities have opportunities to appreciate and participate in cultural and artistic activities from an early age.</p>\r\n<p>Work with art educators, early childhood care and education providers, and primary school teachers and staff to incorporate inclusive art education into their programmes.</p>\r\n<p>Art educators</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Organization</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Early childhood caretakers/education providers</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Organization</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Primary schools</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>School name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Individuals to contact</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Promote awareness</b>\r\n<p>Work with people with disabilities and disabled peoples organizations to develop and run diversity training for staff from a range of cultural and arts programmes to raise awareness about disability and inclusion.</p>\r\n<p>Identify people with disabilities and disabled peoples organizations that would be willing and able to participate in developing this training.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Area(s) of expertise</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Identify cultural and arts programmes whose staff may benefit from training about disability and inclusion:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r2c1 id:cf-140-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r1c2 id:cf-140-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r2c2 id:cf-140-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r3c1 id:cf-140-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text ci_r3c2 id:cf-140-31 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>Promote learning and livelihood opportunities</b>\r\n<p>Work with arts and cultural programmes to develop apprenticeship and employment opportunities for people with disabilities. Ideally, people with disabilities should be provided with opportunities to actively participate in the operation, management and administration of these programmes.</p>\r\n<p>Identify arts and cultural programmes with which your programme may be able to work. For each programme that agrees to participate, ensure that all key staff members are trained on disability and inclusion.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Programme focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Possible apprenticeship or employment opportunities</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Is staff trained on disability and inclusion? (Y/N)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text n_r1c1 id:cf-140-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div cla