ll\" href=\"#v-pills-497\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-497\" aria-selected=\"true\">Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination</a>\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-535-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-535\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-535\" aria-selected=\"true\">Identify local recreation, leisure and sports opportunities</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n\n  <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-497\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-497-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"497\" title=\"Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-535\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-535-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"535\" title=\"Identify local recreation, leisure and sports opportunities\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-10 10:00:00','2019-07-10 10:00:00','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/10/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(537,1,'2019-07-10 10:59:22','2019-07-10 10:59:22','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Facilitate the participation of people with disabilities</b></h4>\r\n<p>Activities are most successful when they are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Requested by individuals and communities</li>\r\n	<li>Culturally appropriate</li>\r\n	<li>Enjoyable and fulfilling for participants</li>\r\n	<li>Not too costly to develop and sustain</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The participation of people with disabilities is facilitated when it is culturally appropriate, enjoyable and fulfilling, and not too costly to develop and sustain.</p>\r\n<p>CBR can do several things to facilitate the participation of people with disabilities in recreation and sporting activities.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<b>1. Identify business-skills training opportunities</b>\r\n<p>Identify local programmes that offer business-skills training. Note that small-enterprise development training programmes often offer this type of training; these can be found in many countries, and are often linked to microfinance schemes.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox ppwd_check1 id:cf-537-1 class:checkbox \"Provide people with disabilities with information about the recreation and sporting opportunities available in their local communities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Use the list of opportunities that you generated in the action step Identify local recreation, leisure and sports opportunities.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox lpwdt_check1 id:cf-537-2 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to mainstream recreation and sporting clubs or associations\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Your CBR programme may need to provide training on disability and inclusion for each of the mainstream recreation and sporting clubs/associations in the community. When doing so, involve people with disabilities as trainers or speakers.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox etcw_check1 id:cf-537-3 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children with disabilities have the same opportunities as other children to participate in recreation and sports activities at school\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Assess the current situation in the primary and secondary schools in your community. What needs to be done so that children with disabilities have the same opportunities as other children?\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>School</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Inclusive and accessible for children with disabilities?</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>What needs to be done?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text schl_r1c1 id:cf-537-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text iaafc_r1c2 id:cf-537-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wntbd_r1c3 id:cf-537-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text schl_r2c1 id:cf-537-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text iaafc_r2c2 id:cf-537-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wntbd_r2c3 id:cf-537-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text schl_r3c1 id:cf-537-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text iaafc_r3c2 id:cf-537-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text wntbd_r3c3 id:cf-537-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eofpp_check1 id:cf-537-13 class:checkbox \"Explore options for providing personal assistance to enable people with disabilities to participate, whether actively or passively\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<p>Identify potential sources of personal assistance:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Personal assistance</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Who would this help most?</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>What could this enable them to do?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea perlass_r1c1 id:cf-537-14 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wwth_r1c2 id:cf-537-15 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wctet_r1c3 id:cf-537-16 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea perlass_r2c1 id:cf-537-17 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wwth_r2c2 id:cf-537-18 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wctet_r2c3 id:cf-537-19 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea perlass_r3c1 id:cf-537-20 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wwth_r3c2 id:cf-537-21 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wctet_r3c3 id:cf-537-22 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea perlass_r4c1 id:cf-537-23 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wwth_r4c2 id:cf-537-24 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea wctet_r4c3 id:cf-537-25 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div 