 inclusion\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-10 11:37:35','2019-07-10 11:37:35','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/10/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(541,1,'2019-07-10 12:13:49','2019-07-10 12:13:49','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Encourage mainstream programmes to become inclusive</b></h4>\r\n<p>Often, mainstream recreation and sports programmes have not considered including people with disabilities. CBR programmes can work with these programmes to explore how to make their activities accessible to all.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR programmes can:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox etpa_check1 id:cf-541-1 class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that programmes are:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Culturally and geographically specific</li>\r\n	<li>Available to people with disabilities of all ages, abilities, and genders</li>\r\n	<li>Available to people living in both urban and rural settings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> National and international organizations may have guidance or resources to support CBR personnel in working with mainstream programmes to ensure inclusion.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox pias_check1 id:cf-541-2 class:checkbox \"Provide ideas and suggestions on how to safely adapt activities, equipment and venues.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>List ideas and suggestions here:</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-100\"><strong>Discriminatory or harmful practices</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disorha_r1c1 id:cf-541-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disorha_r2c1 id:cf-541-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-100\">[text disorha_r3c1 id:cf-541-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox ftfso_check1 id:cf-541-6 class:checkbox \"Facilitate training for staff of mainstream programmes to ensure that they have the skills and confidence needed to include people with disabilities\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<p>Identify persons who can lead these trainings:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text naem_r1c1 id:cf-541-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coinf_r1c2 id:cf-541-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text naem_r2c1 id:cf-541-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coinf_r2c2 id:cf-541-10 class:text class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text naem_r3c1 id:cf-541-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coinf_r3c2 id:cf-541-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<