eed to be aware of and understand the legal rights of people with disabilities. CBR can help promote awareness of these rights in many ways.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>People with disabilities, their family members and other members of the community are often unaware of the legal rights of people with disabilities, and may even mistakenly believe that they do not have any rights.</p>\r\n<p>Your organisation can work to increase awareness of these rights in the following ways:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox ftfso_check1 id:cf-550-1 class:checkbox \"Work with disabled peoples organizations and self-help groups to ensure that people with disabilities and their families are aware of their rights\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<p>Identify the disabled peoples organizations and self-help groups in your area that can assist in this effort:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Group name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Area(s) of focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text grnam_r1c1 id:cf-550-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text asoffo_r1c2 id:cf-550-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninf_r1c3 id:cf-550-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text grnam_r2c1 id:cf-550-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text asoffo_r2c2 id:cf-550-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninf_r2c3 id:cf-550-7 class:text class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text grnam_r3c1 id:cf-550-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text asoffo_r3c2 id:cf-550-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninf_r3c3 id:cf-550-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text grnam_r4c1 id:cf-550-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text asoffo_r4c2 id:cf-550-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text coninf_r4c3 id:cf-550-13 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Note:</b> CBR personnel and members of these groups can work together to hold trainings, meetings, and other activities to ensure that people with disabilities are aware of their legal rights.\r\n<p>Review your database of people with disabilities to ensure that you do not miss anybody.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox diiafod_check1 id:cf-550-14 class:checkbox \"Disseminate information in accessible formats on disability rights, and how to access these rights\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Be sure to provide information in the following forms:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Large print</li>\r\n	<li>Braille</li>\r\n	<li>Audio forms</li>\r\n	<li>Visuals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox piaraaw_check1 id:cf-550-15 class:checkbox \"Participate in awareness-raising activities along with:\"]\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Disabled peoples organizations,</li>\r\n		<li>Self-help groups</li>\r\n		<li>Human rights organizations</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify any existing community activities in which you could participate to raise awareness:\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Organization name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Areas of focus</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgnaem_r1c1 id:cf-550-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text infcon_r1c2 id:cf-550-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aoffo_r1c3 id:cf-550-19 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgnaem_r2c1 id:cf-550-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text infcon_r2c2 id:cf-550-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aoffo_r2c3 id:cf-550-22 class:text class:w-100]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgnaem_r3c1 id:cf-550-23 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text infcon_r3c2 id:cf-550-24 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aoffo_r3c3 id:cf-550-25 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgnaem_r4c1 id:cf-550-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text infcon_r4c2 id:cf-550-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aoffo_r4c3 id:cf-550-2