 informal mechanisms where appropriate</b></h4>\r\n<p>Formal legal processes may not always be the most appropriate mechanism for obtaining justice. Informal mechanisms can often be more effective and are usually quicker, less costly and more accessible for community members.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To help people with disabilities obtain justice through informal means, CBR can:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox elste_check1 id:cf-554-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage local schools to enroll children with disabilities\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div></div></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox atlcarl_check1 id:cf-554-2 class:checkbox \"Approach the local community and religious leaders to help resolve family disputes\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<p>Identify local community or religious leaders with whom your organisation can work:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Affiliation</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea anme_r1c1 id:cf-554-3 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea cint_r1c2 id:cf-554-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea affili_r1c3 id:cf-554-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r