nel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-497-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"497\" title=\"Challenge and address stigma, prejudice and discrimination\"]</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-554\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-554-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"554\" title=\"Promote access to informal mechanisms where appropriate\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-12 07:37:11','2019-07-12 07:37:11','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/12/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(556,1,'2019-07-15 07:51:29','2019-07-15 07:51:29','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Support legal action where appropriate</b></h4>\r\n<p>Sometimes, legal action may be required in order to help people with disabilities attain their legal rights or correct any legal wrongs or damages. CBR can support appropriate legal action in many ways.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To assist people with disabilities in taking legal action where appropriate, CBR programmes can:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox bsraaw_check1 id:cf-556-1 class:checkbox \"Build strong relationships and alliances with trusted members of the legal community\"]</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">\r\n<p>Identify members of the legal community with whom your CBR can work:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Affiliated group(s)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nam1_r1c1 id:cf-556-2 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea coninf1_r1c2 id:cf-556-3 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea affigrp_r1c3 id:cf-556-4 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nam1_r2c1 id:cf-556-5 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea coninf1_r2c2 id:cf-556-6 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea affigrp_r2c3 id:cf-556-7 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nam1_r3c1 id:cf-556-8 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea coninf1_r3c2 id:cf-556-9 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea affigrp_r3c3 id:cf-556-10 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea nam1_r4c1 id:cf-556-11 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea coninf1_r4c2 id:cf-556-12 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea affigrp_r4c3 id:cf-556-13 class:textarea cols:12 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox slatdwl_check1 id:cf-556-14 class:checkbox \"Seek legal advice to determine which legislation is appropriate for addressing different types of discrimination\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox rtdotiw_check1 id:cf-556-15 class:checkbox \"Respect the decision of the individual with disability to seek legal action\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> It can be tempting to take control of the decisions of people with disabilities who seem to be wronged and who may decide on action that does not appear to be best. However, this can further isolate them and minimize the decision-making abilities that they rightfully have.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox rtriit_check1 id:cf-556-16 class:checkbox \"Review the risks involved in taking legal action (particularly where effective legislation and protection mechanisms may not exist)\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Potential risks include:\r\n	<ul><li>Time</li>\r\n		<li>Financial costs</li>\r\n        <li>Security considerations</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox wwtarar_check1 id:cf-556-17 class:checkbox \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their families are involved in legal processes, and are aware of the risks involved\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Work with people with disabilities and their families to help them fully understand the processes and risks involved. Remember that it is important to allow them to make their own decisions.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox laawtw_check1 id:cf-556-18 class:checkbox \"Learn about and work together with organizations that address legal issues for poorer members of the community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify organizations that your organisation should learn more about and can work with:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Area(s) of focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-25\"><strong>Potential ways to work together</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text nam2_r1c1 id:cf-556-19 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf2_r1c2 id:cf-556-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text arcoffc_r1c3 id:cf-556-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text powtwt_r1c4 id:cf-556-22 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text nam2_r2c1 id:cf-556-23 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf2_r2c2 id:cf-556-24 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text arcoffc_r2c3 id:cf-556-25 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text powtwt_r2c4 id:cf-556-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text nam2_r3c1 id:cf-556-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text coninf2_r3c2 id:cf-556-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-25\">[text arcoffc_r3c3 id:cf-556-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical 