ill\" href=\"#v-pills-559\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-559\" aria-selected=\"true\">Carry out a basic communication assessment</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-559\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-559-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"559\" title=\"Carry out a basic communication assessment\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-16 09:21:46','2019-07-16 09:21:46','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/16/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(564,1,'2019-07-16 10:32:27','2019-07-16 10:32:27','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Provide support to develop communication skills</b></h4>\r\n<p>To ensure that people with disabilities are able to develop the communication skills they need, you need to begin by identifying those individuals who have communication impairments.</p>\r\n<p>The types of support your organization will need to provide will depend on the unique needs and circumstances of each of these individuals.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<b>Speech</b>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<p>1. Does your organization work with people who have speech impairments?  Yes  No</p>\r\n<b>if no, skip to question 4.</b>\r\n<p>2. Could any of these individuals benefit from speech and language therapy?  Yes  No</p>\r\n<p>If yes, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to provide referral information for speech and language therapists (enter contact information below:)</p>\r\n[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:100]\r\n<p>3. Do you work with any individuals for whom speech may not be possible?  Yes  No</p>\r\n<p>If yes, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to do the following:</p>\r\n[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Educate family members that speech may not be possible\"]\r\n[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Provide information about other possible ways to communicate (e.g. sign language, communication boards)\"]\r\n[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Make sure that assistive communication devices are available (this may involve showing families how to make devices)\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<b>Hearing</b>\r\n<p>4. Does your organization work with people who have hearing impairments?  Yes  No <b>if no, skip to question 7.</b></p>\r\n<p>5. Could any of these individual(s) benefit from hearing aid(s)?  Yes  No</p>\r\n<p>If yes, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to do the following:</p>\r\n[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Provide information about the availability, fitting, use and care of hearing aids\"]\r\n[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Provide referral information for hearing aid providers (enter contact information below:)\"]\r\n[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:100]\r\n<p>6. Could any of these individual(s) benefit from sign language?  Yes  No</p>\r\n<p>If yes, make sure CBR personnel know where individuals can go to access sign language instruction (enter contact information below:)</p>\r\n[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:100]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n	<b>Environment</b>\r\n	<p>7. Are there barriers to inclusion or acceptance in the community you serve?  Yes  No</p>\r\n	<p>If yes, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to do the following:</p>\r\n	[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Encourage inclusion of people with communication difficulties in everyday activities and experiences (e.g. visits to the market, cooking, cleaning, fetching water)\"]\r\n	[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Teach simple words, phrases and gestures that can be used in the community\"]\r\n	[checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Link disabled individuals to groups, clubs or peer groups that can provide opportunities for social interactions -- for example, deaf clubs, stroke clubs, sports clubs for people with disabilities, inclusive playgroups (enter contact information below:)\"]\r\n	[textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:100]\r\n    [checkbox wwsp_check1 id:cf-511-18 class:checkbox \"Develop decision-making supports (e.g. support for families to learn how to build and maintain support networks), including contacting:\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox elste_check1 id:cf-554-1 class:checkbox \"Legal aid centres\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Name<br> [textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Contact information<br> [textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox elste_check1 id:cf-554-1 class:checkbox \"Lawyers associations\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Name<br> [textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Contact information<br> [textarea ci_r1c2 id:140-2 class:textarea rows:3 cols:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox elste_check1 id