is invalid.','Provide support to develop communication skills','','publish','closed','closed','','provide-support-to-develop-communication-skills','','','2019-07-16 10:38:05','2019-07-16 10:38:05','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=564',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(565,1,'2019-07-16 10:34:10','2019-07-16 10:34:10','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-564-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-564\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-564\" aria-selected=\"true\">Provide support to develop communication skills</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-564\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-564-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"564\" title=\"Provide support to develop communication skills\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-07-16 10:34:10','2019-07-16 10:34:10','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/07/16/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(566,1,'2019-07-18 09:14:01','2019-07-18 09:14:01','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Reduce or remove communication barriers</b></h5>\r\n<p>There are a number of things organizations can do to reduce or remove barriers that make it difficult for disabled people to communicate., including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Conducting an assessment of communication difficulties and needs</li>\r\n<li>Making available material for alternative forms of communication</li>\r\n<li>Providing training in sign language or in language and speech development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following planning tool to identify actions your organization can take to address communication barriers faced by the population you serve. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<b>1. Identify communication barriers</b>\r\n<p>What communication barriers are faced by the disabled individuals that your organization serves?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:100 rows:5]\r\n\r\n<b>2. Select strategies to address these barriers</b>\r\n<p>What communication barriers are faced by the disabled individuals that your organization serves?</p>\r\n\r\n<b>2. Select strategies to address these barriers</b>\r\n<p>Which of the following strategies will be most effective in overcoming the communication barriers identified above? Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to a strategy that you have selected.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Teach family and community members methods for communicating effectively with people who have disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples:<ul>\r\n<li>Allow extra time for communication</li>\r\n<li>Use simple language, gestures, signs, drawings or Braille</li>\r\n<li>Communicate looking directly at the individual</li>\r\n<li>Dont chew gum</li>\r\n<li>Speak normally, without exaggerating your speech or facial expressions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Identify key people with whom disabled people can communicate\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples of potential key communicators include:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Family members</li>\r\n<li>Friends</li>\r\n<li>Neighbours</li>\r\n<li>Teachers</li>\r\n<li>Government officials</li>\r\n<li>Community workers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIdentify potential key communicators:\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n<b>Note:</b> Key communicators must be interested in what disabled people have to say.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Share information with others about disabled people\'s preferred means of communication\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> It is important to develop a means that will enable disabled individuals to communicate independently.</p>\r\n	<p>Example: Create a communication sheet for a person with a disability that informs others the best way to communicate with him or her.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Provide suggestions about how the environment might be adapted to maximize communication\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Examples:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create a quiet space to talk for a person with a hearing impairment</li>\r\n	<li>Provide adequate light for someone who lip-reads</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure that a light is on the face of the non-disabled individual</li>\r\n</ul> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Promote the development of a pool of trained sign language interpreters\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential partner organizations:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Use public meetings or the media to increase community awareness about the challenges faced by people with communication problems\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential media outlets (e.g. radio, television, newspapers) to contact:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-79 id:checkbox class:checkbox12 \"Promote the need for and use of accessible information and communication methods in all activities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential events:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Training events</li>\r\n	<li>Community events</li>\r\n	<li>Development programmes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIdentify potential partner organizations:\r\n[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]	\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from 