 the Management module to learn how to do this), it is important to understand the power structures within the community.</p>\r\n<p><em>Please complete the following form as a first step in understanding the power structure within your community. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>It is important to identify existing power structures because people with power (e.g. religious, political leaders) and influence have the ability to mobilize others to support initiatives in the community. It is also important to understand the current attitudes of these individuals towards people with disabilities so you can determine which individuals and groups are likely to be your strongest supporters.</p>\r\n<p><b>1. People in positions of power</b></p>\r\n<p>Please enter the information requested for key individuals in official positions of power (e.g., local government leaders, leaders of community groups) within your community.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Individual</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Position</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Attitude & behaviour towards people with disabilities</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r2c1 id:cf-574-4 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r2c2 id:cf-574-5 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r2c3 id:cf-574-6 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r3c1 id:cf-574-7 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r3c2 id:cf-574-8 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r3c3 id:cf-574-9 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r4c1 id:cf-574-10 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r4c2 id:cf-574-11 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r4c3 id:cf-574-12 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r5c1 id:cf-574-13 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r5c2 id:cf-574-14 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r5c3 id:cf-574-15 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Organizations</b>\r\n<p>Please enter the information requested for key organizations (e.g., self-help groups, disabled people\'s organizations) with which you will need to work within your community.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Organization</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Key organization member(s)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Attitude & behaviour towards people with disabilities</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r1c1 id:cf-574-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r1c2 id:cf-574-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div