ity\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify local leaders to contact:\r\n	[textarea illtc_r1c2  id:cf-576-2 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox bvaait_r1c1 id:cf-576-3 class:checkbox \"Be visible and active in their communities and support the activities of other stakeholders, such as:\"]\r\n<ul><li>Assisting children to learn in their homes</li>\r\n<li>Providing information on health issues about which people are concerned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify stakeholders who will need support:\r\n	[textarea iswwns_r1c2 id:cf-576-4 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox mcwmds_r1c1 id:cf-576-5 class:checkbox \"Make contact with many different stakeholders in the community to:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get to know them</li>\r\n    <li>Begin to understand their work and their strengths, not just their problems</li>\r\n    <li>Identify along with them the best ways to work with them</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify stakeholders who will need support:\r\n[textarea iswwns_r1c2 id:cf-576-6 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox rsiiaua_r1c1 id:cf-576-7 class:checkbox \"Regularly share important information and updates about CBR\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox bhat_r1c1 id:cf-576-8 class:checkbox \"Be honest and transparent\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox dnmptt_r1c1 id:cf-576-9 class:checkbox \"Do not make promis