ost_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=576',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(577,1,'2019-07-19 11:14:20','2019-07-19 11:14:20','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Raise awareness in the community</b></h5>\r\n<p>There are a number of things organizations can do to raise awareness in the community of the importance of disability rights and concerns.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following planning tool to identify activities your organization can undertake to raise awareness in the community you serve. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Here are some different approaches you can use to create awareness about disability in the community that you serve. Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to each approach that you have selected</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox grpons_r1c1 id:cf-577-1 class:checkbox \"Group discussions\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox rolply_r1c1 id:cf-577-2 class:checkbox \"Role plays\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox flshcrd_r1c1 id:cf-577-3 class:checkbox \"Flash cards\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential resources:\r\n	[textarea idipore_r1c2 id:cf-577-4 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox strling_r1c1 id:cf-577-5 class:checkbox \"Storytelling\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential resources:\r\n	[textarea idepore_r1c2 id:cf-577-6 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<di