rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text poson_r1c2 id:cf-574-2 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Select training topics</b>\r\n<p>Potential training topics:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nSensitization to disability rights and issues\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nOrientation to the CBR strategy\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nHow to deliver CBR training\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nHow to communicate with people with hearing impairments or learning disabilities\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nHow to guide a person with a vision impairment\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Other\"][text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Other\"][text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Other\"][text aabtpw_r1c3 id:cf-574-3 class:text class:w-100]\r\n\r\n<p><b>3. Identify training providers</b></p>\r\n<p>CBR needs to identify existing training programmes in the community and in the local area to conserve and maximize their resources. Following is a list of the types of organizations that often provide training on topics that are useful for community stakeholders. Select the one(s) that your organization may be able to work with.</p>\r\n<b>Organization type</b>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Government agencies\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential government agencies:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:40 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Mainstream development organizations\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential development organizations:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:40 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Non-government