\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r2c1 id:cf-574-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>2. Identify key policies and legislation</b>\r\n<p>Identify key policies and legislation that are related to disability and the development sectors:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Policy/Legislation</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Impact on disability and development sectors</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Action or response required</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r1c1 id:cf-574-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r1c2 id:cf-574-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r2c1 id:cf-574-19 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r2c2 id:cf-574-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r3c1 id:cf-574-22 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r3c2 id:cf-574-23 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-24 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r4c1 id:cf-574-25 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r4c2 id:cf-574-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r5c1 id:cf-574-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r5c2 id:cf-574-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>3. Identify who has the power to make decisions</b>\r\n<p>For each of the key issues related to the disability and development sectors, identify the person(s) or group(s) who has the power to make decisions related to it</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Issue</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Responsibilities that impact the disability and development sectors</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text potio_r1c2 id:cf-574-32 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-33 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r2c1 id:cf-574-34 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-36 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-37 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-39 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-40 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-42 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text invial_r3c1 id:cf-574-43 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text attatpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-45 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>4. Meet regularly with representatives from all political affiliations</b>\r\n<p>CBR programmes need to be nonpartisan. They should not subscribe to, or be thought to subscribe to, a particular party or power-base. It is therefore important to meet regularly with representatives of all political affiliations</p>\r\n<p>List the political affiliations -- and at least one representative of each -- with whom your organization will need to keep in touch</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Political Affiliation</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Representative(s)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text potio_r1c2 id:cf