ies to join literacy programmes\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential literacy programmes:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that people with disabilities have access to advocacy and rights-based training\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential training programmes:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to self-help groups and disabled peoples organizations, where they can learn skills that will be useful for political participation, like public speaking, problem-solving, and campaigning\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Public speaking</li>\r\n	<li>Problem-solving, and</li>\r\n	<li>Campaigning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential self-help groups:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n<p>Identify potential disabled people\'s organizations:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children and adolescents of different impairments are included in activities where they have the opportunity to:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Express their opinions</li>\r\n	<li>Think and make decisions, and</li>\r\n	<li>Understand the consequences of their actions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print