l participation are reduced or removed.</p>\r\n<p><em>Following are some activities designed to help reduce or remove barriers to political participation. Select the one(s) that are most likely to be effective in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Which of the following activities will be most effective in reducing or removing barriers to political participation that are faced by people with disabilities?	Select the ones that you believe will work best in your situation. Please enter additional information where requested next to an activity that you have selected.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Provide recommendations to local authorities about making voting sites and procedures accessible to people with disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify recommendations for making voting more accessible:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Investigate transport options to enable people with disabilities to reach voting venues\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify transport options:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage electoral commissions and advocacy groups to inform voters with disabilities about their voting rights and what types of assistance are available to enable them to participate\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify types of assistance available to enable people with disabilities to participate:\r\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Encourage political leaders and parties to develop accessible campaign materials\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> These should include depictions of voters with disabilities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Identify the political positions and government jobs that are reserved for marginalized groups, and encourage people with disabilities to take apply for them\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify available political positions:\r\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n	Identify available government jobs:\r\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Facilitate access to political processes and decision-making','','publish','closed','closed','','facilitate-access-to-political-processes-and-decision-making','','','2019-08-02 05:53:32','2019-08-02 05:53:32','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=595',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(596,1,'2019-08-02 05:55:07','2019-08-02 05:55:07','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-595-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-595\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-595\" aria-selected=\"true\">Facilitate access to political processes and decision-making</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-595\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-595-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"595\" title=\"Facilitate access to political processes and decision-making\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-08-02 05:55:07','2019-08-02 05:55:07','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/02/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(597,1,'2019-08-02 07:29:13','2019-08-02 07:29:13','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Provide assistance to form new self-help groups</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR can play an active role in creating self-help groups of people with disabilities and their family members. The process of forming self-help groups will vary according to the local situation, with different levels of support required for each group.</p>\r\n<p><em>Please answer the questions below to plan steps your organization can take to support the formation of new self-help groups. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<b>1. Get Started</b>\r\n<p>CBR personnel can provide information about the concept of self-help groups to people with disabilities and their families and encourage them to form a group in their community. They can encourage them to identify and talk with other people in their communities who may be interested in joining and then support in organizing formal planning meetings.</p>\r\n<p>Use the following checklist as a starting point and add your own ideas as needed:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Provide information to people with disabilities and their family members about the concept of self-help groups and encourage them to form a group in their community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Identify potential people to talk to:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\nExamples:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk about the advantages of being in a group</li>\r\n	<li>Talk about the types of concerns that can be addressed, such as:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<ol>Sending children to schools</ol>\r\n    <ol>Providing companionship</ol>\r\n    <ol>Organizing play groups</ol>\r\n	<ol>Learning about government and the benefits available to people with disabilities</ol>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage people with disabilities and their family members to identify and talk with other people in their communities who may be interested in joining\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Identify potential members of the community:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Organize a formal planning meeting in an accessible location\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify potential locations and dates:\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Date</strong></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Discuss what the shared concerns are and establish what the initial focus of the group will be\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Examples:</p>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Sharing feelings and experiences</li>\r\n		<li>Raising awareness</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Ask people what resources they are willing to contribute for the benefit of the group\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Examples:</p>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Physical meeting spaces</li>\r\n		<li>Materials for meetings</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Identify a group leader or coordinator\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify potential tasks and assignments\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <b>Note:</b> It may be necessary to have more than one.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Allocate tasks as early as possible to help promote ownership and responsibility\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify potential tasks and assignments\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Task</strong></div>\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Assigned to</strong></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Establish a group identity by adopting a name for the group\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Identify potential group names:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Decide who can join the group\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Try to keep the group small to begin with as this will provide everyone with a chance to participate.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Decide on how often to meet, setting a date and time for the first meetings\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p><b>Note:</b>Ensure that meetings are arranged in accessible locations and not too far from where the group members live.</p>\r\n<p>Consider holding meetings in community locations (e.g. schools) to ensure visibility of the group and the CBR programme.</p></div></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Arrange escorts for individuals who require assistance to attend meetings\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"If necessary, decide how to publicize the group to encourage people to attend the first meeting.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> This might include talking to people, putting up a poster or advertising on the local radio station or in the newspaper.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>3. Help run the meetings</b>\r\n<p>While CBR personnel are encouraged not to be in charge of running meetings, they need to be aware of the basic structure for a self-help group meeting so they can support and assist groups where necessary. View the basic structure and some ideas of how you can support the groups below. Add additional notes of how else you might be able to support groups in this structure. Keep in mind that each self-help group may choose to run their meetings differently.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Welcoming people to the meeting as they arrive\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Opening the meeting and encouraging members to introduce themselves\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Establishing the rules for confidentiality (for keeping private what is discussed and what happens during a meeting)\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Carrying out the main activities of the meeting\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Identify potential tasks and assignments\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Task</strong></div>\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Assigned to</strong></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Taking minutes of the meetings\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\nExamples\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Record of attendance</li>\r\n	<li>Key topics of discussion</li>\r\n	<li>Key decisions made</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Dealing with administrative matters\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\nExamples\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Date and time of next meeting</li>\r\n	<li>Things to accomplish before next meeting</li>\r\n	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Closing the meeting\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Identify potential supporting tasks:</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>4. Provide facilitation and support</b>\r\n<p>CBR programmes should fulfil a facilitative role in self-help groups, enabling them to work cooperatively and effectively. For example, CBR programmes can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide support and assistance for group leaders when requested</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure meetings are run so that all members understand what is going on and are able to take part</li>\r\n	<li>Encourage the rotation of roles and responsibilities within the group</li>\r\n	<li>Assist the group to see how they can provide mutual support to one another (e.g. companionship, taking children to school, starting group saving activities)</li>\r\n	<li>Check to see that there are fair and transparent methods for sharing the benefits of group activities</li>\r\n	<li>Assist with drafting group rules and regulations once the group is well established</li>\r\n	<li>Provide financial contributions (e.g. seed money or matching grants)</li>\r\n	<p>What are some additional ways that your programme might work with the disabled people\'s organizations that you identified?</p>\r\n    [textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:90 rows:4]</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>5. Build capacity</b>\r\n<p>Groups often need considerable support and capacity-building before they can function effectively and independently.</p>\r\n<b>1. Identify skills that already exist within the group.</b>\r\n<p>Sometimes self-help groups will benefit from the development of specific skills, and sometimes the skills may already exist within the group. Self-help group meetings in themselves provide a good opportunity for members to practice new skills.</p>\r\n<p>Important skills for group members include:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n			<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><ul>\r\n			<li>Preparing agendas</li>\r\n			<li>Conducting meetings</li>\r\n			<li>Ensuring the active participation of all members</li>\r\n			<li>Speaking in public with confidence</li>\r\n			<li>Writing minutes</li>\r\n            \r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">\r\n        	<ul>\r\n        		<li>Resolving conflicts</li>\r\n			   <li>Problem-solving</li>\r\n			   <li>Democratic decision-making</li>\r\n			   <li>Delegation of tasks, and</li>\r\n			   <li>Monitoring progress</li>\r\n		</ul> \r\n	</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    [textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:90 rows:4]</ul>\r\n<p>New self-help groups can learn from already established groups in the community. New groups may benefit from inviting members from existing self-help groups within the community. A new self-help group will value most the experience of people in circumstances similar to their own. Early contact between self-help groups of people with disabilities is important for learning, future links and mutual help.</p>\r\n<p>Groups may be hesitant about getting involved in social or political action at first because they feel they lack the know-how or ability. But with time, patience and encouragement, group members will begin to discover their ability to understand, plan and implement the activities needed to change their situation.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Provide assistance to form new self-help groups','','publish','closed','closed','','provide-assistance-to-form-new-self-help-groups','','','2019-08-02 07:38:02','2019-08-02 07:38:02','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=597',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(598,1,'2019-08-02 07:30:12','2019-08-02 07:30:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-597-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-597\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-597\" aria-selected=\"true\">Provide assistance to form new self-help groups</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-597\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-597-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"597\" title=\"Provide assistance to form new self-help groups\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-08-02 07:30:12','2019-08-02 07:30:12','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/02/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(600,1,'2019-08-05 06:11:13','2019-08-05 06:11:13','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Develop partnerships with existing self-help groups</b></h4>\r\n<p>Existing self-help groups often have similar goals to new groups started through CBR. Because of this, it is important to identify and make contact with any groups that currently exist in the community so you can work towards developing partnerships to share knowledge and resources and to ensure that more people with disabilities and their families are reached.</p>\r\n<p><em>Use the planning tool below to identity existing self-help groups, and to begin to develop a strategy for working with them. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<b>1. Identify existing self-help groups</b>\r\n<p>Identify some existing self-help groups near your community and the contact personnel for each group:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Group Focus</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r1c1 id:cf-574-16 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r1c2 id:cf-574-17 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r2c1 id:cf-574-19 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r2c2 id:cf-574-20 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r2c3 id:cf-574-21 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r3c1 id:cf-574-22 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r3c2 id:cf-574-23 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r3c3 id:cf-574-24 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r4c1 id:cf-574-25 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r4c2 id:cf-574-26 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r4c3 id:cf-574-27 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text orgxzt_r5c1 id:cf-574-28 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text komem_r5c2 id:cf-574-29 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r5c3 id:cf-574-30 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text aabtpwd_r1c3 id:cf-574-18 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>2. Develop an outreach strategy</b>\r\n<p>CBR can reach out to the self-help groups in various ways. Use the list of potential outreach activities below as a starting point for planning an outreach and partnership strategy. Keep in mind that the groups may not know what CBR is and that you may need to help them understand the CBR approach.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Hold an informational session about what CBR is and how it benefits the community and disabled peoples and families.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify potential locations and dates:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Date</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea s1_r1c1 id:cf-511-1 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea l1_r1c2 id:cf-511-2 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea s1_r2c1 id:cf-511-4 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea l1_r2c2 id:cf-511-5 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea s1_r3c1 id:cf-511-7 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea l1_r3c2 id:cf-511-8 class:textarea cols:20 rows:2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Identify and present some goals on which your programme and the self-help groups can work together, including some things that CBR can offer.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify partnership goals:<br>\r\n	[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\r\n<p><b>Note:</b> Each group will have their own goals and it is important to strategize together with each group to build a partnership that is beneficial to both sides.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>3. Contact groups and build partnerships</b>\r\n<p>After you have planned an outreach and partnership strategy, you can reach out to the self-help groups to introduce CBR and the prospect of working together. Be sure to have a consistent follow-up with the groups to maintain your working relationship. From this point, you may work together to identify new partnership goals or activities, or plan additional programming, events, or more.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Develop partnerships with existing self-help groups','','publish','closed','closed','','develop-partnerships-with-existing-self-help-groups','','','2019-08-05 06:42:10','2019-08-05 06:42:10','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=600',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(601,1,'2019-08-05 06:12:34','2019-08-05 06:12:34','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-600-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-600\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-600\" aria-selected=\"true\">Develop partnerships with existing self-help groups</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-600\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-600-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"600\" title=\"Develop partnerships with existing self-help groups\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-08-05 06:12:34','2019-08-05 06:12:34','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/05/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(602,1,'2019-08-05 07:25:17','2019-08-05 07:25:17','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Encourage inclusion of people with disabilities in mainstream groups</b></h4>\r\n<p>WWhile self-help groups specifically for people with disabilities and their families play an important role, CBR should also encourage people with disabilities and their families to become members of mainstream self-help groups.</p>\r\n<p><em>Use the planning tool below to identify and develop new ways to encourage inclusion. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>This checklist can be used as a starting point for you to think of ways to encourage inclusion. You can develop your own ideas and add them to this list.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Encourage mainstream self-help groups to include people with disabilities as regular members with equal rights.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> All meetings must take place in accessible venues.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Educate mainstream groups about the needs and potential of people with disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Note:</b> Positive role-models can contribute significantly to this effort.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Highlight common issues faced by people both with and without disabilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some common issues:\r\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\r\n        <b>Example:</b>\r\n        <ul><li>Facilitate a discussion about gender discrimination with a womens group and highlight how this issue is shared by all women</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Identify existing members of mainstream self-help groups who are either disabled or have a family member who is disabled. Encourage these people to talk about the issues they face, and put disability on the agenda of their self-help group for discussion\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some potential people:\r\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\r\n        \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox cb_1 id:cf-511-1 class:checkbox1 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their families are informed about objectives and goals of relevant mainstream groups\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Identify some potential skill or knowledge gaps:\r\n		[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]<br>\r\n   		<b>Note:</b> Without the necessary skills and knowledge, people with disabilities may be vulnerable to discrimination\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\n