you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-604-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-604\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-604\" aria-selected=\"true\">Encourage self-help group members to participate in CBR programmes</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-604\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-604-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"604\" title=\"Encourage self-help group members to participate in CBR programmes\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-08-05 07:51:04','2019-08-05 07:51:04','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/05/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(606,1,'2019-08-05 08:32:10','2019-08-05 08:32:10','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Encourage self-help groups to join together</b></h4>\r\n<p>While self-help groups for people with disabilities and their family members may be able to make a difference at the local level, their members may be limited in capacity to make changes at higher levels.</p>\r\n<p>Greater numbers of people can bring about change and therefore the next step is to encourage self-help groups (both those that have been started by CBR programmes and those that exist independently) to come together under one \"umbrella\". This is commonly known as a federation.</p>\r\n<p><em>Use the planning tool below to think about some strategies for facilitating the formation of a self-help group federation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Self-help group federations need to ensure that people of different groups (e.g. of different age, impairment, gender, socioeconomic status) are equally represented. A self-help group federation can also take on greater responsibilities, and one day may become a formal organization in its own right.</p>\r\n<p>CBR programmes can facilitate the formation of a self-help group federation in various ways. One key way is to bring together one or two elected representatives from each self-help group.</p>\r\n<b>1. Identify some potential representatives from each self-help group.</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Self-help group</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Potential representatives</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<b>2. Organize and facilitate an initial discussion</b>\r\n<p>The next step is to have a time and space for an initial discussion between representatives of the self-help groups. During the meeting, CBR personnel can facilitate the conversation and help groups to understand each other. Here are some possible topics of discussion for such a meeting:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>General introductions</li>\r\n	<li>Describe each groups focus, current work, and goals, and find common ground</li>\r\n	<li>Highlight any existing joint foci, work, and goals</li>\r\n	<li>Brainstorm any new joint goals</li>\r\n	<li>Discuss and list out the possible benefits of working together - e.g. additional resources, connections, and joint influence</li>\r\n	<li>Identify and discuss next steps in working together</li>\r\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\r\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\r\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\r\n	<li>[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:94 rows:1]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You can modify this suggested list of topics of discussion as needed for the self-help groups that you work with.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, identify some potential meeting times and locations:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Meeting Date and Time</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Meeting Location</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea ideiso_r1c2 id:cf-570-7 class:textarea cols:45 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical