h one, indicate which group(s) of people may benefit from that service.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Type of service</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>People who may not benefit</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Identify the barriers faced by those in need of these services</b>\r\n<p>Now identify what barriers current members of disabled peoples organizations may face in accessing these services, as well as potential solution(s) for overcoming those barriers. Two possible responses are shown below as examples.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Type of service</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>People who may not benefit</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Disabled person does not know of the service provided.</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Advertise that service within the disabled peoples organization.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Disabled person does not have a way to physically access the service due to limited mobility or distance.</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><em>Example:</em> Set up some form of transportation to enable the disabled person to travel to the necessary location.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<