t.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Encourage disabled peoples organizations to support CBR as a strategy','','publish','closed','closed','','encourage-disabled-peoples-organizations-to-support-cbr-as-a-strategy','','','2019-08-06 09:53:51','2019-08-06 09:53:51','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=613',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(614,1,'2019-08-06 09:50:12','2019-08-06 09:50:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!---------- SOCIAL--->\n<div class=\"accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Social</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n<div class=\"accordion sub-accordion\">\n<div class=\"accordion-title\">Relationships, marriage and family</div>\n<div class=\"accordion-desc clear-both\">\n\n\n<div class=\"nav flex-column nav-pills tab-menu\" id=\"v-pills-tab\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\n <a class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"v-pills-613-tab\" data-toggle=\"pill\" href=\"#v-pills-613\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"v-pills-613\" aria-selected=\"true\">Encourage disabled peoples organizations to support CBR as a strategy</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-content tab-content-wrap\" id=\"v-pills-tabContent\">\n\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"v-pills-613\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"v-pills-613-tab\">[contact-form-7 id=\"613\" title=\"Encourage disabled peoples organizations to support CBR as a strategy\"]</div>\n\n \n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-08-06 09:50:12','2019-08-06 09:50:12','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/06/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(615,1,'2019-08-07 05:45:35','2019-08-07 05:45:35','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h4><b>Support the formation of community-based disabled peoples organizations</b></h4>\r\n<p>A community based disabled peoples organization has many strengths, as they are in direct contact with people with disabilities at the grassroots level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are multiple things that your organisation can do to support disabled people in your local community who are interested in starting a disabled peoples organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<em>Complete the following planning tool to think through some things your organization can do to support the formation of disabled peoples organizations in the community you serve. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em>\r\n\r\n<b>1. Identify disabled people in your community who may be interested in forming a disabled peoples organization</b>\r\n<p>Enter the names of people who may be interested in forming an organization below.</p>\r\n<p><b>Note:</b> Make sure there is representation from:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Women and children with disabilities</li>\r\n	<li>All impairment groups (especially people with severe or multiple impairments), and</li>\r\n	<li>People from different socioeconomic groups</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Possible people</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Type of organization they are interested in forming</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>2. Provide information about the benefits of forming a disabled peoples organization</b>\r\n<p>Your CBR programme may need to provide information about the benefits of forming a disabled peoples organization. To do this, you may choose to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Distribute pamphlets or brochures</li>\r\n	<li>Hold information sessions, or</li>\r\n	<li>Hold smaller meetings with the people who are interested in forming their own group.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>List some ways that your organization will provide this information below.</p>\r\n<p><b>Note:</b> It is important to make a clear distinction between the roles and responsibilities of CBR programmes and those of disabled peoples organizations, while highlighting how the two can work together.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Method of sharing information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Persons to share with</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>When it will happen</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:27 rows:4]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>3. Provide support to disabled peoples organizations</b>\r\n<p>Once people in the community do begin to form disabled peoples organizations, your CBR organization should continue supporting their efforts in many ways. Here are some ways that CBR programmes can support disabled peoples organizations. Select the one(s) that your organization can use; then enter some others of your own.</p>\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Work in partnership with disabled peoples organizations at the national or regional level to organize training to build the capacity of potential members of disabled peoples organizations\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Assist with the activities needed to form a new disabled peoples organization, such as:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Developing their organizational structure, mission, objectives, and plan of action</li>\r\n	<li>Registering with the local authorities</li>\r\n	<li>Opening bank accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Completing any other necessary legal formalities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Provide ongoing assistance once the disabled peoples organization is formed, such as inviting local members to training sessions carried out by CBR programmes so that they can observe stakeholders attitudes towards disability issues\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Assist in identifying desired changes and in creating a plan to make them happen\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Help organization members identify other disabled peoples organizations at various levels with which they may wish to link\"]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 [textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13][textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:90 rows:1]\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-263 id