:14:15','2019-08-07 08:14:15','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Promote mental health</b></h5>\r\n<p>There are several socio-economic and political determinants of mental health, such as poverty, violence, neglect, and sexual abuse. To promote mental health, CBR programmes should address these determinants in partnership with relevant sectors.</p>\r\n<p><em>Use the planning tool to get started in promoting mental health in your community. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Use this checklist as a starting point and add your own ideas:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Create inclusive environments that respect and protect the basic rights of everyone, including people with mental health problems.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>What are some characteristics that you aim to have in such an inclusive environment?</p>\r\n[textarea khtu_r1c2 id:cf-572-17 class:textarea cols:45 rows:4]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Strengthen community networks and encourage collective responsibility for preventing:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alcohol/drug abuse,</li>\r\n	<li>Gender discrimination, and</li>\r\n	<li>Community and family violence</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Identify some existing community networks to focus partnerships on:\r\n</p>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Networks</strong></div>\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Contact person</strong></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Develop partnerships with other stakeholders that are involved in promoting mental health and well-being.\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Some examples include:</p>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Work with womens clubs on gender issues</li>\r\n		<li>Work with a local non-governmental organization to focus on early interventions with children</li>\r\n		<p>Identify potential partners and activities:</p>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Stakeholders</strong></div>\r\n		<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical w-50\"><strong>Possible activities</strong></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n		<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n        <div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[text indual_r1c1 id:cf-574-1 class:text class:w-100]</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Promote positive interactions between parents and their children to enhance childhood development.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p>Examples:</p>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Play with children in developmentally appropriate ways</li>\r\n		<li>Involve children in everyday activities, such as chores</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Promote evidence-based programmes in schools that enhance the social and emotional competencies of students to help prevent substance abuse and violence.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p><b>Note:</b> Some examples may be found at </p>	\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox eacfe_r1c1 id:cf-572-1 class:checkbox \"Work with the media to change the negative image of people with mental health problems.\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><p><b>