"page-number\">\r\n 	 Page 4/40\r\n </div>\r\n<div class=\"w-100 p-3 clear-both\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row border border-dark\">\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n	<p class=\"p-3\">This section provides a brief overview of CBR, its history and the CBR Guidelines</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Female_0.jpg\" alt=\"about the guidenes\">\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<img class=\"w-100\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/introduction_new_0.jpg\"  alt=\"About the guidelines splash image\" style=\"\r\n    padding-top: 22px;\r\n\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n','About the guidelines','','publish','closed','closed','','about-the-guidelines','','','2019-08-09 10:25:06','2019-08-09 10:25:06','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=629',0,'chapters','',0),(630,1,'2019-08-09 06:47:39','2019-08-09 06:47:39','<div class=\"w-100 p-3 border border-dark h-100 clear-both\">\n<div class=\"col-md-10\">\n	<p>This section provides a brief overview of CBR, its history and the CBR Guidelines</p>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"col-md-2\">\n	<img src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Female_0.jpg\" alt=\"about the guidenes\">\n	</div>\n\n\n\n	<div>\n		<img src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/introduction_new_0.jpg\"  alt=\"About the guidelines splash image\"></div>\n</div>\n','About the guidelines','','inherit','closed','closed','','629-autosave-v1','','','2019-08-09 06:47:39','2019-08-09 06:47:39','',629,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/08/629-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(631,1,'2019-08-09 08:01:03','2019-08-09 08:01:03','<div class=\"page-number\">\r\n 	 Page 5/40\r\n </div>\r\n<div>\r\n 	<p>As defined in a <a href=\"http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/43060/1/9241592389_eng.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Joint Position Paper on community-based rehabilitation (CBR)</a> issued in 2004:</p>\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n <div class=\"row border\" style=\"padding:10px; border:1px solid #ccc; margin:10px 0px; background-color:#efefef;\"><p>CBR is a strategy within general community development for rehabilitation, equalization of opportunities and social inclusion for all people with disabilities.</p></div>\r\n\r\n <div><p>For an overview of the connections between CBR and community-based inclusive development <a href=\"http://iddcconsortium.net/sites/default/files/resources-tools/files/brochure_summary_bat.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">click here</a></p></div>','What is community-based rehabilitation?','','publish','closed','closed','','what-is-community-based-rehabilitation','','','2019-08-09 10:26:19','2019-08-09 10:26:19','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=631',0,'chapters','',0),(632,1,'2019-08-09 08:58:18','2019-08-09 08:58:18','<div class=\"page-number\">\r\n 	 Page 6/40\r\n </div>\r\n<div><p>Community-based rehabilitation is implemented through the combined efforts of:</p>\r\n<div style=\"line-height:32px;\"><ul>\r\n	<li>people with disabilities themselves</li>\r\n	<li>their families, organizations and communities, and</li>\r\n	<li>relevant governmental and nongovernmental agencies and organizations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Who is involved in community-based rehabilitation?','','publish','closed','closed','','who-is-involved-in-community-based-rehabilitation','','','2019-08-09 10:26:45','2019-08-09 10:26:45','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=632',0,'chapters','',0),(633,1,'2019-08-09 09:08:54','2019-08-09 09:08:54','<div><p>Community-based rehabilitation is implemented through the combined efforts of:</p>\n<div  style=\"line-height: 20px;\"><ul>\n	<li>people with disabilities themselves</li>\n	<li>their families, organizations and communities, and</li>\n	<li>relevant governmental and nongovernmental agencies and organizations.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>','Who is involved in community-based rehabilitation?','','inherit','closed','closed','','632-autosave-v1','','','2019-08-09 09:08:54','2019-08-09 09:08:54','',632,'http://include.xyz/2019/08/09/632-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(634,1,'2019-08-09 09:33:56','2019-08-09 09:33:56','<div class=\"page-number\">\r\n 	 Page 7/40\r\n </div>\r\n<div><p>Community-based rehabilitation (CBR) was endorsed by WHO following the Declaration of Alma-Ata in 1978. At that time, CBR was seen as a strategy to improve access to rehabilitation services for people with disabilities in low- and medium-resource countries. Over the past 30 years, however, its scope has broadened considerably. Currently, CBR is implemented in over 100 countries.</p>\r\n 	<em>Key events in the development of CBR are shown in the timeline below. Position your cursor over each point in the timeline to learn more.</em></div>','History of CBR','','publish','closed','closed','','history-of-cbr','','','2019-08-09 10:59:15','2019-08-09 10:59:15','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=634',0,'chapters','',0),(635,1,'2019-08-09 10:43:33','2019-08-09 10:43:33','   <div class=\"page-number\">\r\n 	 Page 8/40\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"w-100 p-3 clear-both\">\r\n 	<div class=\"row\">\r\n 	<div class=\"col-md-10\"><p>The material presented in INCLUDE is based on the CBR Guidelines, which were released in 2010 by WHO. All materials have been updated to incorporate significant developments since the guidelines were released.</p>\r\n\r\n 	<p>The CBR Guidelines were based on the <a href=\"#dr-alwan\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#dr-alwan\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CBR Matrix</a> which had been developed in 2004 to provide a common framework for CBR. INCLUDE is also based on this framework.</p>\r\n\r\n 	<p>View the <a href=\"http://www.who.int/disabilities/cbr/guidelines/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">original CBR Guidelines</a></p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-2\"><img alt=\"Photo of the printed CBR Guidelines\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/cbr_guidelines.jpg\" style=\"height:140px; width:111px\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n 	\r\n </div>','The CBR Guidelines','','publish','closed','closed','','the-cbr-guidelines','','','2019-08-09 13:12:47','2019-08-09 13:12:47','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=635',0,'chapters','',0),(636,1,'2019-08-09 10:42:09','2019-08-09 10:42:09','','cbr_guidelines','','inherit','open','closed','','cbr_guidelines','','','2019-08-09 10:42:09','2019-08-09 10:42:09','',0,'http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/cbr_guidelines.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(637,1,'2019-08-09 11:28:08','2019-08-09 11:28:08','<div class=\"page-number\">\r\n	Page 9/40\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"w-100 p-3 clear-both\">\r\n\r\n	<p>The overall objectives of the CBR Guidelines are as follows.</p>\r\n	<div class=\"clear-both\">\r\n\r\n		<div class=\"img-container float-right\"><img alt=\"Photo of the printed CBR Guidelines\" src=\"http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/objectives-of-guidelines.jpg\">\r\n        <div class=\"caption\">\r\n		<span>WHO/Khasnabis</span>\r\n	</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n		<div class=\"\">\r\n			<ul class=\"module-ul-li li\">\r\n				<li>Provide guidance showing how to develop and strengthen CBR in line with the CBR Joint Position Paper and the CRPD.</li>\r\n				<li>Promote CBR as a strategy for community-based inclusive development involving people with disabilities.</li>\r\n				<li>Support stakeholders in meeting the basic needs and enhancing the quality of life of people with disabilities and their families by facilitating access to health, education, livelihood and social services.</li>\r\n				<li>Encourage stakeholders to facilitate the empowerment of people with disabilities and their families by promoting their inclusion and participation in development and decision-making processes on an equal basis with others.</li>\r\n				<li>Propose a strategy to develop community support services that will enable people with disabilities to live independently and be included in the community, in accordance with article 19 of the CRPD.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','Objectives of the guidelines','','publish','closed','closed','','objectives-of-the-guidelines','','','2019-08-09 13:13:22','2019-08-09 13:13:22','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=chapters&#038;p=637',0,'chapters','',0),(638,1,'2019-08-09 11:28:41','2019-08-09 11:28:41','','objectives-of-guidelines','','inherit','open','closed','','objectives-of-guidelines','','','2019-08-09 11:28:41','2019-08-09 11:28:41','',0,'http://include.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/objectives-of-guidelines.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0);
